Vidim ih!

4
00:02:25,209 --> 00:02:25,729
Tatice!

5
00:02:32,091 --> 00:02:33,131
Kako si, duso?

6
00:02:33,968 --> 00:02:35,818
Drago mi je sto te vidim.

7
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:16,070
- Zdravo.
- Kako si?

8
00:03:18,362 --> 00:03:20,352
- Sladak je. Divan.
- Hvala.

9
00:03:22,338 --> 00:03:23,388
Moramo krenuti.

10
00:03:23,976 --> 00:03:27,426
- Da, moramo krenuti.
- Trebala bih ti dati broj.

11
00:03:27,493 --> 00:03:30,633
Ne vracam se u Chicago.
Idem na Cape, pa...

12
00:03:30,251 --> 00:03:32,641
Isti pansion kao lani?
Imam broj.

13
00:03:36,108 --> 00:03:37,508
Sine, pozdravi mamu.

14
00:03:38,752 --> 00:03:40,002
- Pusa.
- Pa-pa, mama.

15
00:03:03,372 --> 00:03:04,062
Volim te.

16
00:03:44,793 --> 00:03:46,183
Nazovi me. Kad god.

17
00:03:46,472 --> 00:03:48,052
- 'Djenja.
- Volim te.

18
00:04:00,188 --> 00:04:01,178
'Djenja, mama.

19
00:04:38,499 --> 00:04:39,959
Oprostite sto kasnim.

20
00:04:44,121 --> 00:04:46,831
Financijski savjetnik.
Nedavno razveden.

21
00:04:52,407 --> 00:04:54,917
Vidjela si kako
je pojeo palacinke?

22
00:04:57,004 --> 00:04:58,984
Polako je jeo svaki zalogaj.

23
00:04:58,438 --> 00:04:59,188
Saberi se.

24
00:05:01,063 --> 00:05:03,923
Znas sto kazu za
visoke mrsave muskarce?

25
00:05:04,022 --> 00:05:05,482
Imaju golema stopala.

26
00:05:06,758 --> 00:05:07,278
'Jutro.

27
00:05:09,249 --> 00:05:12,399
Znam da jutros ide u
kazaliste, na matineju.

28
00:05:12,779 --> 00:05:14,519
Ja idem u obilazak luke.

29
00:06:37,099 --> 00:06:38,209
"Draga Catherine

30
00:06:38,685 --> 00:06:41,605
Zao mije sto tako
dugo nismo razgovarali.

31
00:06:42,101 --> 00:06:43,561
Osjecam se izgubljeno

32
00:06:44,614 --> 00:06:46,364
... bez smjera i kompasa.

33
00:06:46,454 --> 00:06:49,434
Nalijecem na stvari.
Malo sam lud, mislim:

34
00:06:53,197 --> 00:06:55,477
Nikad prije
nisam bio izgubljen.

35
00:06:56,136 --> 00:06:57,756
Ti si bila moj Sjever.

36
00:07:00,671 --> 00:07:04,101
Dok si ti bila moj dom,
uvijek sam nalazio put.

37
00:07:03,581 --> 00:07:06,611
Oprosti sto sam bio
gnjevan kad si otisla.

38
00:07:06,956 --> 00:07:09,636
Jos mislim da je
doslo do pogreske...

39
00:07:11,096 --> 00:07:13,246
... i cekam da je Bog ispravi.

40
00:07:16,842 --> 00:07:18,282
No sad mi je bolje.

41
00:07:18,752 --> 00:07:19,792
Rad mi pomaze.

42
00:07:22,099 --> 00:07:23,839
A najvise mi pomazes ti.

43
00:07:26,195 --> 00:07:29,322
Sinoc si mi dosla u
snove sa svojim smijeskom...

44
00:07:29,816 --> 00:07:32,626
... koji me uvijek grlio
kao ljubavnika.

45
00:07:32,623 --> 00:07:34,193
Ljuljao me kao dijete.

46
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:37,920
Od sna pamtim samo...

47
00:07:38,817 --> 00:07:39,987
... osjecaj mira.

48
00:07:46,128 --> 00:07:47,928
Probudio sam se s njim...

49
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,550
... i pokusao ga odrzati na zivotu.

50
00:07:51,975 --> 00:07:54,935
Pisem ti da sam na
putu prema tome miru.

51
00:07:57,426 --> 00:08:00,206
I da ti kazem da
za mnogo toga zalim.

52
00:08:02,287 --> 00:08:05,317
Zalim sto se nisam
bolje brinuo za tebe...

53
00:08:04,727 --> 00:08:08,467
... pa da nikad ne bi bila
prestrasena ili bolesna. "

54
00:08:15,577 --> 00:08:18,704
"Zao mi je sto se nisam vise trudio
da nadjem rijeci...

55
00:08:18,313 --> 00:08:20,189
... da ti kazem sto osjecam.

56
00:08:20,183 --> 00:08:22,684
Zao mi je sto nisam
popravio vrata verande.

57
00:08:23,094 --> 00:08:24,544
Sad sam ih popravio.

58
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:26,930
Zao mi je za svaku nasu svadju.

59
00:08:29,083 --> 00:08:31,933
Zao mi je sto se
nisam vise ispricavao.

60
00:08:31,453 --> 00:08:32,703
Bio sam preponosan.

61
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:36,827
Zao mi je sto ti nisam
davao vise komplimenata...

62
00:08:36,730 --> 00:08:39,540
... na tvojoj odjeci i
tvojim frizurama.

63
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:42,807
Zao mi je sto te nisam drzao
takvom snagom...

64
00:08:42,405 --> 00:08:44,907
... da te cak ni Bog
ne bi mogao odvuci. "

65
00:08:45,091 --> 00:08:46,661
Potpis:
"Voli te G. "

66
00:08:49,048 --> 00:08:50,318
To je tako tuzno.

67
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,190
Nije samo to. ako je...

68
00:08:54,622 --> 00:08:55,442
... iskreno.

69
00:08:57,419 --> 00:08:59,869
Moglo bi biti staro stotinu godina.

70
00:08:59,504 --> 00:09:00,784
Otipkano je, Alva.

71
00:09:05,707 --> 00:09:06,757
Prilicno dobro.

72
00:09:07,751 --> 00:09:10,252
To znaci da zelis
da si ga ti napisao.

73
00:09:09,867 --> 00:09:11,743
Ja bih ga poslao "e-mailom ".

74
00:09:11,361 --> 00:09:13,111
Svejedno, znam sto zelis.

75
00:09:13,692 --> 00:09:16,032
Da je naslovljeno " Draga Teresa".

76
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:18,990
Ma daj, Charlie.

77
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:22,010
Svaka cura zeli biti tako voljena.

78
00:09:22,773 --> 00:09:24,703
Biti neciji " pravi Sjever"?

79
00:09:24,858 --> 00:09:25,608
Salite se?

80
00:09:28,499 --> 00:09:30,079
Osobito usamljene zene?

81
00:09:30,899 --> 00:09:31,939
Tako me vidis?

82
00:09:32,801 --> 00:09:35,781
Razgovarala si s kime?
Ispricala koji vic?

83
00:09:36,208 --> 00:09:37,458
Dobro sam se provela.

84
00:09:38,191 --> 00:09:38,711
Doista?

85
00:09:39,626 --> 00:09:41,366
Vratila si se dan prije.

86
00:09:41,497 --> 00:09:42,717
Volim svoj posao.

87
00:09:44,244 --> 00:09:46,754
To je poricanje.
Trebala bi pisati.

88
00:09:47,447 --> 00:09:49,948
Nadaj se da cu se drzati istrazivanja.

89
00:09:49,614 --> 00:09:51,490
Bez mene ne bi mogao
pisati svoju kolumnu.

90
00:09:52,522 --> 00:09:57,132
Primijetila si da mi se ovdje iz
postovanja obracaju s g. Toschi?

91
00:09:57,009 --> 00:10:00,136
Poznavala sam te prije nego
sto si stavio navlake na zube.

92
00:10:00,213 --> 00:10:03,813
I ja tebe kad si bila ziva
koraka i puna radosti.

93
00:10:03,303 --> 00:10:07,233
Al Giddons, " Lakefront Winter",
Harcourt-Brace, 1948. g.

94
00:10:09,130 --> 00:10:11,450
Mislio sam da sam to ja smislio.

95
00:10:33,624 --> 00:10:35,014
Hej, Jase! Kako si?

96
00:10:35,708 --> 00:10:36,458
Bok, Lina.

97
00:10:37,031 --> 00:10:38,121
Ne, zao mi je.

98
00:10:41,374 --> 00:10:43,064
Ocekivala sam da nazove.

99
00:10:44,324 --> 00:10:46,724
Nisam zabrinuta. Samo mi nedostaje!

100
00:10:47,049 --> 00:10:47,449
Znam.

101
00:10:50,702 --> 00:10:51,272
Sto je?

102
00:10:53,702 --> 00:10:55,792
Ne, tek sam ga dobila. Zasto?

103
00:10:59,153 --> 00:10:59,723
Sto je?

104
00:11:05,101 --> 00:11:06,791
Pronadjena Poruka U Boci

105
00:11:10,122 --> 00:11:12,562
Ne mogu vjerovati da je to ucinio.

106
00:11:07,745 --> 00:11:09,025
Ne mogu vjerovati!

107
00:11:11,335 --> 00:11:14,462
- Zasto si tako uzrujana?
- Jer je pogresno tiskati to!

108
00:11:13,135 --> 00:11:16,805
Nije u redu! Osobno je!
To su necije intimne misli.

109
00:11:20,977 --> 00:11:22,427
To nije tvoje pismo!

110
00:11:21,923 --> 00:11:24,653
Da, znam da nije.
Ja sam ga pronasla.

111
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:26,022
Ovo postaje osobno? Zato si tako ljuta?

112
00:11:26,296 --> 00:11:27,986
Nisam ljuta. Samo sam...

113
00:11:29,743 --> 00:11:30,793
... malo ljuta.

114
00:11:56,769 --> 00:11:59,219
Imao si priliku na Bozicnoj zabavi.

115
00:11:58,661 --> 00:11:59,651
'Jutro, lutko.

116
00:12:01,682 --> 00:12:02,612
Pogledaj ovo.

117
00:12:04,276 --> 00:12:06,956
Pisma novinama o poruci
u boci. Vidi.

118
00:12:06,949 --> 00:12:07,289
Sto?

119
00:12:08,456 --> 00:12:10,958
I jos dvije kutije.
Nosi u istrazivanje.

120
00:12:11,264 --> 00:12:13,765
Nasla sam ih u sobi za postu.
Lijepa ritica.

121
00:12:13,846 --> 00:12:16,348
Charlie zeli da ostavimo sve ostalo.

122
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:18,296
I da odgovorimo na sva ova?

123
00:12:18,016 --> 00:12:20,996
Pregledat cemo ih.
Zbrojiti "za i protiv".

124
00:12:21,566 --> 00:12:22,816
Baciti sva ludjacka.

125
00:12:22,858 --> 00:12:26,611
Tiskat cemo izvatke. Gazde zele
da to iskoristimo. Veliko je.

126
00:12:27,807 --> 00:12:30,308
Vece od skandala
s dijetnim kolacima.

127
00:12:30,127 --> 00:12:32,629
Vece od gradonacelnika
i uciteljice.

128
00:12:32,839 --> 00:12:33,419
Cudesno.

129
00:12:33,289 --> 00:12:35,099
"Vasa je kolumna grozna. "

130
00:12:35,568 --> 00:12:36,819
- Negativno.
- Cuj ovo.

131
00:12:37,278 --> 00:12:39,779
" Kad bi vise muskaraca
imalo osjecajnosti i hrabrosti...

132
00:12:39,546 --> 00:12:42,066
... da kazu sto osjecaju,
umjesto...

133
00:12:42,492 --> 00:12:44,994
... da se skrivaju iza
sportskih programa... "

134
00:12:44,658 --> 00:12:46,698
" Necakinja mi je to poslala.

135
00:12:49,545 --> 00:12:51,421
Mislim da je poruka istoj osobi...

136
00:12:50,614 --> 00:12:52,884
... i saljem vam je u prilogu. "

137
00:12:53,797 --> 00:12:54,257
Molim?

138
00:12:56,257 --> 00:12:56,597
Sto?

139
00:12:58,292 --> 00:12:59,543
" Draga Catherine. "

140
00:13:00,135 --> 00:13:01,645
Ne. Salis se? Doista?

141
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,640
Na glas. Citaj na glas.

142
00:13:07,527 --> 00:13:11,147
" Draga Catherine. U mom
zivotu nema sata bez tebe.

143
00:13:11,534 --> 00:13:13,409
Popravljam brodove,
provjeravam ih...

144
00:13:13,974 --> 00:13:17,374
... a cijelo vrijeme uspomene
naviru poput plime.

145
00:13:18,489 --> 00:13:20,365
Danas sam mislio o
danima nase mladosti...

146
00:13:21,196 --> 00:13:24,166
... a ti si napustila nas
svijet za veci.

147
00:13:24,063 --> 00:13:27,033
Vise sam se bojao
nego sto sam priznavao.

148
00:13:27,337 --> 00:13:29,213
Borio sam se
protiv svog straha...

149
00:13:29,382 --> 00:13:32,509
... govorivsi sebi da ces
se jednog dana vratiti...

150
00:13:32,107 --> 00:13:35,860
... i mislio sam sto cu ti
prvo reci kad te opet vidim.

151
00:13:36,337 --> 00:13:39,027
Mora da sam iskusao
tisucu mogucnosti.

152
00:13:40,385 --> 00:13:42,065
Sto sam na kraju rekao?

153
00:13:42,368 --> 00:13:43,298
Nista veliko.

154
00:13:44,218 --> 00:13:48,008
Usta mi se nisu kretala,
mogao sam te samo poljubiti.

155
00:13:48,418 --> 00:13:50,758
ad si rekla:
' Ostajem zauvijek'.

156
00:13:50,921 --> 00:13:52,131
To je sve reklo.

157
00:13:53,290 --> 00:13:54,680
Evo, opet to cinim.

158
00:13:57,470 --> 00:14:02,140
Ponovno zamisljam sto cu ti reci
ako mi se nekada budes vratila. "

159
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:04,060
Bobe, Teresa iz Tribunea:

160
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:07,890
Da. Znam da je dugo proslo.

161
00:14:07,985 --> 00:14:09,725
Cuj, imam nesto za tebe.

162
00:14:09,684 --> 00:14:10,434
Dva traga.

163
00:14:11,597 --> 00:14:14,337
Pismo je na sluzbenom papiru
sa zigom.

164
00:14:14,423 --> 00:14:16,693
I kako da otkrijem pisaci stroj?

165
00:14:16,936 --> 00:14:18,812
Pisaci stroj koji trazis: : :

166
00:14:19,235 --> 00:14:21,345
... jest Olimpic Herzfogen 980.

167
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:22,329
Njemacki. Star.

168
00:14:23,964 --> 00:14:26,934
Je li se taj stroj
prodavao u ducanima...

169
00:14:26,414 --> 00:14:28,290
... u SAD-u u
posljednjih 30 g. ?

170
00:14:28,794 --> 00:14:30,314
Batici su zamijenjeni.

171
00:14:30,778 --> 00:14:34,238
Ljudi koji vole strojeve
kupuju ovakve obnovljene.

172
00:14:33,971 --> 00:14:37,591
Ovo je pismo vjerojatno
napisano u posljednjih 5 g.

173
00:14:37,552 --> 00:14:39,062
Znaci on negdje zivi.

174
00:14:39,769 --> 00:14:40,979
I mozda je mlad.

175
00:14:41,599 --> 00:14:42,850
Svidjet ce ti se ovo.

176
00:14:43,604 --> 00:14:46,105
Sjecas se sto si me trazila?
Dosli su nalazi o cepu.

177
00:14:45,709 --> 00:14:47,959
U vodi je bio
negdje oko 2 g.

178
00:14:48,536 --> 00:14:49,856
To je sve? 2 g. ?

179
00:14:50,968 --> 00:14:51,658
Hvala ti.

180
00:14:54,771 --> 00:14:56,022
Ne ocekuj to i od mene.

181
00:14:56,144 --> 00:14:57,364
Staklo boje vode.

182
00:14:57,222 --> 00:14:57,622
89...

183
00:14:58,645 --> 00:14:59,925
... izgleda kao A.

184
00:15:00,384 --> 00:15:01,774
No saljem ti fotke.

185
00:14:32,144 --> 00:14:32,944
Boca Br. 1

186
00:14:35,898 --> 00:14:36,698
Boca Br. 2

187
00:14:37,149 --> 00:14:38,249
Cini se sjajno:

188
00:15:16,533 --> 00:15:17,983
Svidja ti se dijete?

189
00:15:18,566 --> 00:15:19,786
Uvijek si zauzet.

190
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:22,210
Nikad nemamo prilike razgovarati.

191
00:15:22,573 --> 00:15:24,683
- Prekini!
- Jase, cekaj malo.

192
00:15:25,906 --> 00:15:30,285
Sjecas se pisma o poruci iz boce
na zidu restorana u Virginiji?

193
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:31,041
Papir, logotip, pisaci
stroj, sve je ovdje.

194
00:15:32,953 --> 00:15:36,080
Prekini i ukljuci peticu.
Ona ceka da razgovara s tobom.

195
00:15:35,741 --> 00:15:38,868
- Nikad ne mogu razgovarati s njim.
- Nazovi ga.

196
00:15:39,809 --> 00:15:41,060
Moze li ga faksirati?

197
00:15:41,101 --> 00:15:43,602
Faksirati?To je Virginia.
Mali provincijski restoran.

198
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:45,060
Otkud da znam
ima li ona faks?

199
00:15:44,579 --> 00:15:45,739
Neka ti faksira.

200
00:15:46,187 --> 00:15:46,757
U redu.

201
00:15:47,886 --> 00:15:50,506
Dobro. Ne.
Pricaj mi o Bunker Hillu.

202
00:15:58,490 --> 00:16:00,992
"Svim brodovima na
moru i svim lukama.

203
00:16:00,941 --> 00:16:04,291
Mojoj obitelji, svim
prijateljima i neznancima. "

204
00:16:03,942 --> 00:16:06,443
- Nema " Draga Catherine"?
- Ne, ovaj put nema.

205
00:16:05,946 --> 00:16:08,326
No papir i pisaci
stroj su isti.

206
00:16:10,156 --> 00:16:14,176
Mislimo da je to prva ili
posljednja poruka. Je li tako?

207
00:16:14,286 --> 00:16:16,146
" Ovo je poruka i molitva.

208
00:16:16,655 --> 00:16:19,782
Poruka je da su me moja
putovanja naucila velikoj istini.

209
00:16:19,747 --> 00:16:22,597
Vec sam imao ono
sto svi drugi traze...

210
00:16:23,001 --> 00:16:24,861
... a malo tko ikad nadje:

211
00:16:25,138 --> 00:16:28,265
Jednu osobu koju
sam rodjen voljeti zauvijek.

212
00:16:28,556 --> 00:16:31,058
Osobu poput mene.
S Outer Banksa...

213
00:16:31,069 --> 00:16:32,945
... tajnovitu poput
modrog Atlantika. "

214
00:16:32,989 --> 00:16:34,865
Outer Banks.
o je u Sjevernoj Carolini.

215
00:16:34,505 --> 00:16:37,005
Jest. Ali to je oko
tucet gradova.

216
00:16:36,652 --> 00:16:40,332
Ali samo 4 dovoljno velika
za brodogradnju i remont.

217
00:16:41,502 --> 00:16:42,542
Onda ga imamo.

218
00:16:44,055 --> 00:16:47,182
Ondje imamo dopisnike.
Nas list je u Wilmingtonu.

219
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:49,600
Kladim se da cemo ga
pronaci prije kraja tjedna.

220
00:16:49,709 --> 00:16:50,579
ko prihvaca?

221
00:16:54,346 --> 00:16:54,916
Sto je?

222
00:16:56,166 --> 00:16:56,791
Ja zelim ici.

223
00:16:58,108 --> 00:16:59,558
Ona zeli to uciniti.

224
00:16:59,481 --> 00:17:01,356
Pronaci ces tipa i sto onda?

225
00:17:01,251 --> 00:17:04,379
Ne znam. Nisam sigurna.
No znam da zelim ici.

226
00:17:03,204 --> 00:17:05,764
Ne mogu te pustiti.
rebam te ovdje.

227
00:17:07,466 --> 00:17:10,726
Poslao si me u lndiju
po clanak o dimnjacima.

228
00:17:11,555 --> 00:17:15,307
Poslao si je da u eksasu
tri dana razgovara s Marincima.

229
00:17:15,145 --> 00:17:16,535
o je bilo drukcije.

230
00:17:17,505 --> 00:17:19,075
Zasto moras to osobno?

231
00:17:19,275 --> 00:17:21,777
Kako osobno?
Zaintrigirana sam. Pa sto?

232
00:17:21,554 --> 00:17:22,494
Zaintrigirana?

233
00:17:23,222 --> 00:17:25,098
Sto ako je tip
pokriven tetovazama...

234
00:17:25,795 --> 00:17:28,296
... i odsluzio je
4 zatvorske kazne?

235
00:17:28,001 --> 00:17:29,391
Reci joj. Hoces li?

236
00:17:30,330 --> 00:17:31,490
Samo se bojim...

237
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:33,740
... da previse ocekujes.

238
00:17:33,769 --> 00:17:36,270
Nista ne ocekujem.
Ovo je istrazivanje.

239
00:17:37,704 --> 00:17:41,104
Zamisljas si Heatcliffa.
Pa si zamisljas Hamleta.

240
00:17:40,694 --> 00:17:42,904
A tip je zacijelo kapetan Ahab.

241
00:17:44,265 --> 00:17:45,825
Kazes da ne mogu ici?

242
00:17:49,685 --> 00:17:51,185
To je rizik, zar ne?

243
00:17:52,553 --> 00:17:54,223
To mi govoris vec 2 g.

244
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,630
" Riskiraj. "

245
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:58,034
Trazila si da nazovem: : :

246
00:17:59,083 --> 00:18:01,483
... sve papirnice
na Outer Banksu.

247
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:05,430
- Imam druga imena za tebe. Cekaj.
- Pronasla sam.

248
00:18:05,501 --> 00:18:07,011
Sto? Sto si pronasla?

249
00:18:07,127 --> 00:18:08,997
Nazvala sam Moorehead City.

250
00:18:08,502 --> 00:18:11,003
Rekli su mi da se sjecaju
Iogotipa s malom jedrilicom.

251
00:18:10,962 --> 00:18:14,052
Rekli su mi da su ga
dizajnirale musterije.

252
00:18:16,861 --> 00:18:17,601
o su oni.

253
00:18:18,885 --> 00:18:20,345
Nemoj reci Charlieju.

254
00:18:19,872 --> 00:18:22,373
Natjerat ce te da
ovo obavis telefonom.

255
00:18:21,815 --> 00:18:22,975
Imas ga, heresa.

256
00:18:24,673 --> 00:18:26,473
Idi, pokucaj mu na vrata.

257
00:19:53,770 --> 00:19:54,230
Gospo?

258
00:19:57,676 --> 00:19:58,546
Mogu pomoci?

259
00:20:00,951 --> 00:20:03,701
Oprostite.
Samo se divim starim kucama.

260
00:20:05,131 --> 00:20:06,711
Bavite se nekretninama?

261
00:20:08,375 --> 00:20:08,655
Ne.

262
00:20:11,873 --> 00:20:13,623
Smijem li slikati kucu...

263
00:20:14,671 --> 00:20:15,661
... za novine?

264
00:20:16,369 --> 00:20:17,479
Jehovin svjedok?

265
00:20:19,602 --> 00:20:21,702
Fotograf. oga se nisam sjetio.

266
00:20:23,266 --> 00:20:25,142
Ne mogu reci ni da ni ne.

267
00:20:24,985 --> 00:20:25,445
Zasto?

268
00:20:26,633 --> 00:20:28,073
o je kuca mog sina.

269
00:20:29,176 --> 00:20:30,746
Ja zivim tamo dolje...

270
00:20:31,047 --> 00:20:31,747
... ondje.

271
00:20:32,817 --> 00:20:34,507
Morat cete pitati njega.

272
00:20:35,106 --> 00:20:37,606
Naci cete ga u luci.
Garret Blake.

273
00:20:38,839 --> 00:20:40,229
Nikad ne nosi kapu.

274
00:20:41,056 --> 00:20:42,046
Sjajno. Hvala.

275
00:20:44,829 --> 00:20:46,099
Je li za Playboy?

276
00:20:47,687 --> 00:20:49,563
Divim se vasim naslovnicama.

277
00:20:49,893 --> 00:20:51,633
No nikad ga nisam kupio.

278
00:20:55,263 --> 00:20:56,723
Uvijek postoji sutra.

279
00:21:28,487 --> 00:21:29,737
Divan dan, zar ne?

280
00:21:29,849 --> 00:21:32,351
Krasan.
Volio bih da mogu biti na vodi.

281
00:21:32,352 --> 00:21:33,282
Mogu misliti.

282
00:21:37,253 --> 00:21:39,128
Sjajan brod. Popravljate ga?

283
00:21:39,308 --> 00:21:40,818
rudim se koliko mogu.

284
00:21:43,457 --> 00:21:44,557
Zivite od toga?

285
00:21:45,471 --> 00:21:47,391
Ne, bavim se time vikendom.

286
00:21:48,593 --> 00:21:50,813
Imate brod koji treba popraviti?

287
00:21:50,158 --> 00:21:50,858
Zapravo...

288
00:21:51,724 --> 00:21:54,414
Ovdje imam covjeka
koji ima radionicu.

289
00:21:57,064 --> 00:21:58,940
Radi ondje na drvenoj skuni.

290
00:21:58,419 --> 00:22:00,979
Dugacka je 12 m.
Krasnog je oblika.

291
00:22:01,194 --> 00:22:03,070
Nema boljih od starih drvenjaka.

292
00:22:03,381 --> 00:22:04,371
Sjajno, hvala.

293
00:22:04,754 --> 00:22:07,794
- Nema na cemu. Ugodan vam dan.
- Takodjer.

294
00:22:35,192 --> 00:22:37,062
Volim stare drvene brodove.

295
00:22:38,171 --> 00:22:40,311
Ovaj ima 12 m? Skuna, zar ne?

296
00:22:42,891 --> 00:22:43,761
Alden skuna.

297
00:22:44,347 --> 00:22:45,857
G. 1922. , iz Mainea.

298
00:22:49,786 --> 00:22:50,126
Vas?

299
00:22:52,137 --> 00:22:52,537
Nije.

300
00:22:54,424 --> 00:22:55,704
Samo ga uredjujem.

301
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,630
Krasne linije.

302
00:23:03,112 --> 00:23:04,392
Zelite se ukrcati?

303
00:23:11,004 --> 00:23:12,284
Ima nesto lokvica.

304
00:23:22,921 --> 00:23:23,611
Divan je.

305
00:23:25,859 --> 00:23:27,479
Bio je u losem stanju?

306
00:23:27,548 --> 00:23:28,248
Zanemaren.

307
00:23:29,053 --> 00:23:29,813
Necijenjen.

308
00:23:31,871 --> 00:23:33,671
Znam kakav je to osjecaj.

309
00:23:34,211 --> 00:23:34,791
Sumnjam.

310
00:23:38,278 --> 00:23:38,978
Turistica?

311
00:23:40,211 --> 00:23:42,311
Samo upoznajem mjesto i ljude.

312
00:23:44,441 --> 00:23:45,141
Theresa...

313
00:23:46,688 --> 00:23:47,508
... Osborne.

314
00:23:48,835 --> 00:23:49,765
Garret Blake.

315
00:23:50,758 --> 00:23:52,908
Zvucite kao da ste sa sjevera.

316
00:23:52,976 --> 00:23:53,496
Doista?

317
00:23:54,878 --> 00:23:55,688
Iz Chicaga.

318
00:23:56,596 --> 00:23:58,176
Bavim se istrazivanjem.

319
00:23:58,825 --> 00:23:59,225
Cega?

320
00:24:01,927 --> 00:24:03,147
Svega. Za novine.

321
00:24:05,822 --> 00:24:08,672
Mogu li gdje jedriti
sad kad sam ovdje?

322
00:24:10,651 --> 00:24:12,527
S druge strane mozete
unajmiti brod.

323
00:24:13,305 --> 00:24:15,405
Ne, nije to,
nisam iskusna...

324
00:24:15,370 --> 00:24:16,070
... uopce.

325
00:24:17,538 --> 00:24:19,288
Zeljela bih biti. Samo...

326
00:24:20,345 --> 00:24:22,865
Dolazim iz " Prerijske drzave", pa...

327
00:24:25,410 --> 00:24:26,740
Na vodi sam truba.

328
00:24:30,759 --> 00:24:33,509
Oprostite sto sam vas prekinula.
Hvala.

329
00:24:38,304 --> 00:24:39,994
Sutra cu malo isploviti.

330
00:24:40,969 --> 00:24:43,419
Pokusna plovidba.
Do rta i natrag.

331
00:24:44,326 --> 00:24:45,486
Oko sat vremena.

332
00:24:46,350 --> 00:24:47,860
Ako zelite sa mnom...

333
00:24:48,966 --> 00:24:50,066
Bilo bi lijepo.

334
00:24:52,476 --> 00:24:53,226
Oko sedam.

335
00:24:54,093 --> 00:24:54,613
Sjajno!

336
00:24:56,924 --> 00:24:58,324
Ako dodjete prije...

337
00:24:58,418 --> 00:25:00,294
... bit cu u onoj zalogajnici.

338
00:25:00,414 --> 00:25:01,634
Prije sedam sati?

339
00:25:03,232 --> 00:25:04,922
Sjajno. Vidimo se ovdje.

340
00:25:06,589 --> 00:25:07,219
Ili u...

341
00:25:08,044 --> 00:25:09,274
... u zalogajnici.

342
00:25:43,111 --> 00:25:44,211
Chete, kako si?

343
00:25:44,221 --> 00:25:45,451
- Dobro.
- Isuse!

344
00:25:45,636 --> 00:25:48,836
Ovdje su ti svaki dan isti ljudi.
Svaki dan.

345
00:25:54,152 --> 00:25:56,322
uristi idu u
" Palacinkarnicu".

346
00:25:55,496 --> 00:25:55,896
Neka.

347
00:25:58,427 --> 00:26:00,927
A sto ti imas?
Uvijek iste ribare.

348
00:26:01,204 --> 00:26:02,454
Nadobudnog stolara.

349
00:26:03,392 --> 00:26:05,152
I kratkovidnog mehanicara.

350
00:26:05,427 --> 00:26:08,177
e lopova koji zeli
biti brodograditelj.

351
00:26:10,259 --> 00:26:12,189
Ne zapocinji sranja, Johnny.

352
00:26:12,457 --> 00:26:15,967
Lopov je onaj koji zadrzava
sebi tudje vlasnistvo.

353
00:26:16,363 --> 00:26:17,173
Imam pravo?

354
00:26:17,766 --> 00:26:20,966
Nemas pravo ako sud kaze
da nemas pravo. Ne?

355
00:26:24,014 --> 00:26:25,064
Lajavi seronja.

356
00:26:25,112 --> 00:26:26,092
Sto si rekao?

357
00:26:26,914 --> 00:26:29,004
Kako si znao da govorim tebi?

358
00:26:30,150 --> 00:26:31,480
Ne. Zvat cu Petea.

359
00:26:32,582 --> 00:26:35,262
Opet razbijte lokal
i tuzit cu vas...

360
00:26:34,310 --> 00:26:36,760
... i bit ce uhicenja. Ne blefiram!

361
00:26:40,425 --> 00:26:42,585
Lopov zasluzuje biti u zatvoru.

362
00:26:42,958 --> 00:26:46,086
Nikad nista nisam uzeo tebi
ni ma komu u ovom gradu.

363
00:26:46,458 --> 00:26:49,585
- Ja tvrdim drugo.
- A ti si lazljivac, Johnny.

364
00:26:49,491 --> 00:26:51,061
Ne zovi me lazljivcem!

365
00:26:53,663 --> 00:26:55,003
Dajte, zgrabite ga!

366
00:27:00,092 --> 00:27:01,662
Hocete ih vec primiti?

367
00:27:01,914 --> 00:27:03,374
Dajte, razdvojite ih.

368
00:27:07,785 --> 00:27:09,535
Garrete, dodji. Pusti ga.

369
00:27:09,647 --> 00:27:10,107
Dodji!

370
00:27:12,385 --> 00:27:13,485
Prekini s time.

371
00:27:15,335 --> 00:27:16,675
Jednom samo otidji.

372
00:27:17,818 --> 00:27:19,158
Nije toga vrijedan.

373
00:27:19,833 --> 00:27:20,293
Hajde.

374
00:27:23,252 --> 00:27:24,932
Vidio si sto je ucinio?

375
00:27:26,265 --> 00:27:27,425
Hajde, smiri se.

376
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:29,696
- Smiri se, Johnny.
- Idi, Garrete.

377
00:27:29,083 --> 00:27:31,543
- Nije vrijedan toga.
- Pustite me!

378
00:27:31,932 --> 00:27:32,682
Gotovo je.

379
00:27:58,955 --> 00:28:00,755
Mislio sam da neces doci.

380
00:28:01,276 --> 00:28:03,306
Dosla sam reci da necu doci.

381
00:28:06,231 --> 00:28:09,441
Nisam htjela samo ne doci.
Mrzim takve ljude.

382
00:28:10,259 --> 00:28:12,339
Zao mi je sto si to vidjela.

383
00:28:12,803 --> 00:28:14,053
o se ovdje cesto dogadja?

384
00:28:15,621 --> 00:28:17,201
Umjesto kuglanja ili...

385
00:28:22,447 --> 00:28:24,077
Dobro, mozda se vidimo.

386
00:28:24,991 --> 00:28:26,741
Svejedno idem na pokusnu.

387
00:28:29,051 --> 00:28:30,161
Kratka plovidba.

388
00:28:31,595 --> 00:28:34,445
Ne znam. Sto ako se
razljutite na mene?

389
00:28:34,616 --> 00:28:35,656
Brod je malen.

390
00:28:36,835 --> 00:28:38,645
Ne volim tucnjave, heresa.

391
00:28:40,296 --> 00:28:41,166
Ni kuglanje.

392
00:28:44,234 --> 00:28:46,110
Prije nego sto odes, hoces...

393
00:28:46,116 --> 00:28:48,276
... odvezati ono i dobaciti mi?

394
00:28:49,474 --> 00:28:50,284
Cijenim to.

395
00:29:03,300 --> 00:29:03,760
Hvala.

396
00:29:28,133 --> 00:29:30,043
Gdje ti necu biti na putu?

397
00:29:30,661 --> 00:29:31,931
Obici cu ja tebe.

398
00:29:46,107 --> 00:29:47,437
A da ipak izadjem?

399
00:29:48,737 --> 00:29:49,947
Zao mi je, ja...

400
00:29:51,129 --> 00:29:53,049
Bio sam vjestiji s ljudima.

401
00:29:54,949 --> 00:29:56,169
Bio si sarmantan?

402
00:29:57,920 --> 00:30:00,240
Zao mi je sto sam to propustila.

403
00:30:30,009 --> 00:30:31,929
ko je covjek u zalogajnici?

404
00:30:33,610 --> 00:30:34,940
To je stari sukob.

405
00:30:35,615 --> 00:30:36,895
Ne zelim njuskati.

406
00:30:38,036 --> 00:30:38,906
Koliko star?

407
00:30:44,424 --> 00:30:46,414
Cime se bavis? Istrazivanjem?

408
00:30:48,473 --> 00:30:50,453
Zapravo ne. Ovo je razgovor.

409
00:30:53,477 --> 00:30:55,697
Mozda mogu pomoci. Imam diplomu.

410
00:30:58,606 --> 00:31:00,806
Ukrao si mu curu u 8. razredu?

411
00:31:02,553 --> 00:31:02,833
Ne.

412
00:31:05,118 --> 00:31:07,148
Vjencao sam mu se s sestrom.

413
00:31:09,799 --> 00:31:11,049
Sad si ti na redu.

414
00:31:11,264 --> 00:31:11,834
Zar ne?

415
00:31:14,458 --> 00:31:15,668
Jos ste u braku?

416
00:31:18,568 --> 00:31:18,788
i?

417
00:31:22,170 --> 00:31:22,920
Imam sina.

418
00:31:24,479 --> 00:31:25,409
Sjajnog sina.

419
00:31:27,104 --> 00:31:28,094
Cesto izlazis?

420
00:31:30,697 --> 00:31:30,917
i?

421
00:31:34,114 --> 00:31:35,990
Napokon si shvatio kako to ide.

422
00:31:36,638 --> 00:31:38,788
Pazi da te debelnjak ne udari.

423
00:32:21,248 --> 00:32:22,628
Cuo si se s mamom?

424
00:32:25,124 --> 00:32:26,284
Dobio sam pismo.

425
00:32:28,016 --> 00:32:29,346
Jos joj nisi drag.

426
00:32:31,922 --> 00:32:32,732
Ma stvarno?

427
00:32:41,190 --> 00:32:42,580
Premala je za tebe.

428
00:32:43,701 --> 00:32:44,041
Sto?

429
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:45,970
Vjetrovka.

430
00:32:50,134 --> 00:32:50,534
Koja?

431
00:32:51,315 --> 00:32:52,835
- Njezina je.
- Cija?

432
00:32:53,095 --> 00:32:54,835
Zene koja je danas bila.

433
00:32:55,089 --> 00:32:56,829
Ostavila ju je na brodu.

434
00:32:58,651 --> 00:33:00,621
Rekao si joj? Nazvao si je?

435
00:33:00,930 --> 00:33:01,390
Nisam.

436
00:33:02,721 --> 00:33:05,331
Mislio sam da je ti odneses u hotel.

437
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:09,470
Necu nositi jaknu. Nosi je ti.

438
00:33:10,881 --> 00:33:13,031
Sto? Ne zelis je opet vidjeti?

439
00:33:16,508 --> 00:33:16,968
Mozda.

440
00:33:18,137 --> 00:33:18,417
Pa?

441
00:33:19,835 --> 00:33:21,515
Pa, tata, nije to lako.

442
00:33:25,173 --> 00:33:26,093
Budi ti ona.

443
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,470
Ja cu biti ti.

444
00:33:29,437 --> 00:33:30,547
Tvoja vjetrovka.

445
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:36,130
Takve vjetrovke...

446
00:33:36,966 --> 00:33:38,766
... ne vide se svaki dan.

447
00:33:51,136 --> 00:33:51,776
Trenutak.

448
00:34:01,095 --> 00:34:02,346
Zaboravila si ovo.

449
00:34:02,194 --> 00:34:02,654
Hvala.

450
00:34:04,361 --> 00:34:06,941
Nisam izlazila.
Nisam ni primijetila.

451
00:34:07,027 --> 00:34:07,487
Hvala.

452
00:34:10,315 --> 00:34:11,065
Hoces uci?

453
00:34:19,967 --> 00:34:20,717
Lijepo je.

454
00:34:22,716 --> 00:34:24,526
Viktorijansko, iz 1911. g.

455
00:34:25,340 --> 00:34:27,380
Konaciste je postalo 1944. g.

456
00:34:28,301 --> 00:34:28,761
Ali...

457
00:34:29,848 --> 00:34:32,058
... ti si zacijelo sve to znao.

458
00:34:33,104 --> 00:34:34,674
Nikad nisam bio ovdje.

459
00:34:35,851 --> 00:34:36,361
Pa da.

460
00:34:37,510 --> 00:34:39,250
Zasto bi bio? Odavde si.

461
00:34:40,339 --> 00:34:42,019
Ovo je tvoj rodni grad.

462
00:34:45,568 --> 00:34:47,778
Danas mi je doista bilo lijepo.

463
00:34:49,811 --> 00:34:51,061
I brod se dobro ponio.

464
00:34:52,619 --> 00:34:54,899
Nismo morali iskakati ili slicno.

465
00:34:59,751 --> 00:35:01,627
Hvala sto si donio vjetrovku.

466
00:35:02,254 --> 00:35:03,234
Nema na cemu.

467
00:35:05,286 --> 00:35:07,788
Znam da sam ti se
osam puta zahvalila...

468
00:35:08,298 --> 00:35:10,688
... jer nemam pojma sto bih rekla.

469
00:35:11,157 --> 00:35:15,097
Pitam se zasto si tu,
jer ni ti ne znas sto bi rekao.

470
00:35:15,462 --> 00:35:16,782
I ja se to pitam.

471
00:35:25,726 --> 00:35:26,536
Jedes meso?

472
00:35:29,349 --> 00:35:29,989
Govedinu?

473
00:35:31,394 --> 00:35:31,914
Katkad.

474
00:35:33,776 --> 00:35:35,596
Pripremam savrsene odreske.

475
00:35:36,950 --> 00:35:38,690
To je najbolje sto znam.

476
00:35:43,187 --> 00:35:44,647
- Hvalis se.
- Znam.

477
00:35:45,659 --> 00:35:46,699
Ali istina je.

478
00:35:48,549 --> 00:35:50,939
Zanimljivo. Hvala sto si mi rekao.

479
00:35:54,509 --> 00:35:56,385
Rado bih ti ga pripremio...

480
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:57,490
... sutra navecer.

481
00:35:57,879 --> 00:35:58,399
Doista?

482
00:36:04,115 --> 00:36:05,745
Znas, danas na brodu...

483
00:36:08,267 --> 00:36:10,127
... i meni je bilo lijepo.

484
00:36:17,271 --> 00:36:18,371
