503
00:37:33,855 --> 00:37:36,425
- Mogu ti natociti casu?
- Molim te.

504
00:37:41,688 --> 00:37:42,558
Sjajna kuca.

505
00:37:44,822 --> 00:37:45,812
Ovo svjetlo...

506
