Vjetar.

509
00:38:08,183 --> 00:38:09,293
Mjesni umjetnik?

510
00:38:10,951 --> 00:38:12,411
Moja zena, Catherine.

511
00:38:14,319 --> 00:38:16,299
Umrla je prije dvije godine.

512
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:20,990
Moja sucut.

513
00:38:53,325 --> 00:38:54,245
I ti slikas?

514
00:39:03,846 --> 00:39:06,346
Moj je tata umro dok sam studirala.

515
00:39:06,767 --> 00:39:09,047
Mama je cuvala njegovu kosulju...

516
00:39:10,286 --> 00:39:12,976
