521
00:40:06,825 --> 00:40:08,975
Ali cuj,
nesto ti moram reci.

522
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:11,580
I ja sam bio zivcan.

523
00:40:14,689 --> 00:40:15,499
Samo sam...

524
00:40:19,432 --> 00:40:19,772
Sto?

525
00:40:26,634 --> 00:40:27,214
Nisam...

526
00:40:29,933 --> 00:40:30,913
Ne cinim ovo.

527
00:40:32,091 --> 00:40:32,901
Hvala Bogu.

528
00:40:33,443 --> 00:40:34,823
Ni ja to ne cinim.

529
00:40:35,183 --> 00:40:36,273
Ne ide mi ovo.

530
00:40:42,244 --> 00:40:45,674
Za dvoje ljudi koji ovo
ne cine, dobro nam ide.

531
00:40:51,870 --> 00:40:53,850
Dovoljno je hladno za vatru?

532
00:41:01,982 --> 00:41:04,432
Mislila sam da smo jos zaljubljeni:

533
00:41:05,544 --> 00:41:07,534
Mozda nisam ni razmisljala...

534
00:41:07,672 --> 00:41:10,242
... jer imala sam sina,
posao, muza.

535
00:41:12,545 --> 00:41:14,355
Trebala sam postati pisac.

536
00:41:15,049 --> 00:41:16,029
David i ja...

537
00:41:17,319 --> 00:41:20,069
... smo razgovarali
i o drugom djetetu.

538
00:41:21,062 --> 00:41:22,172
Mozes vjerovati?

539
00:41:25,104 --> 00:41:27,084
Jednog dana sam se vozila...

540
00:41:29,511 --> 00:41:30,791
