Sjedila sam u autu. Nisam ugasila
motor. Samo sam sjedila...

546
00:41:51,207 --> 00:41:52,657
... jedno sat i pol.

547
00:41:57,972 --> 00:41:59,662
Suocen si s nemogucim...

548
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:03,230
... i treba ti sat i pol da shvatis.

549
00:42:10,692 --> 00:42:12,892
Bio je s njom vec godinu dana.

550
00:42:21,456 --> 00:42:24,426
Ne mogu vjerovati da
sam ti to ispricala.

551
00:42:25,588 --> 00:42:27,618
To se svima dogadja, zar ne?

552
00:42:31,511 --> 00:42:33,841
Ali sad se dogodilo tebi, heresa.

553
00:42:37,321 --> 00:42:38,121
Zao mi je.

554
00:42:44,433 --> 00:42:46,693
Dogadja li se to u St. Claireu?

555
00:42:46,661 --> 00:42:48,751
Sve se dogadja u St. Claireu.

556
00:42:52,391 --> 00:42:53,201
S vremenom.

557
00:43:01,558 --> 00:43:03,128
Pricaj mi o Catherine.

558
00:43:09,108 --> 00:43:09,508
Pa...

559
00:43:12,842 --> 00:43:14,242
Odrasli smo zajedno.

560
00:43:15,427 --> 00:43:16,467
Ona je bila...

561
00:43:21,961 --> 00:43:24,361
Ljude je privlacio njezin osmjeh...

562
00:43:25,666 --> 00:43:27,196
... njezin entuzijazam.

563
00:43:29,674 --> 00:43:32,494
Mogla je razveseliti
cijelu prostoriju...

564
00:43:32,239 --> 00:43:33,349
... cijeli grad.

565
00:43:40,157 --> 00:43:42,137
Zvao sam je Sveta Catherine.

566
00:43:47,614 --> 00:43:48,654
Kako je umrla?

567
00:43:53,953 --> 00:43:55,113
Bila je bolesna.

568
00:43:57,779 --> 00:43:58,819
Bila je krhka.

569
00:44:00,578 --> 00:44:01,378
Zao mi je.

570
00:44:05,686 --> 00:44:06,486
U redu je.

571
00:44:07,182 --> 00:44:07,752
U redu.

572
00:44:09,952 --> 00:44:11,828
Cijeli zivot si zivio ovdje?

573
00:44:11,579 --> 00:44:12,149
Jos ne.

574
00:44:14,917 --> 00:44:15,847
Ovo mjesto...

575
00:44:18,194 --> 00:44:20,696
