Kad mi je bilo 10 g. ,
odvela me u Virginiju.

579
00:44:27,108 --> 00:44:29,128
No vratio sam se sa 16 g...

580
00:44:31,087 --> 00:44:32,837
... i vise nisam odlazio.

581
00:44:33,316 --> 00:44:35,066
Nedostajalo mi je. Miris.

582
00:44:36,288 --> 00:44:37,208
Rad na vodi.

583
00:44:38,404 --> 00:44:39,974
Nedostajao mi je tata.

584
00:44:42,466 --> 00:44:42,926
isina.

585
00:44:45,377 --> 00:44:45,897
Vjetar.

586
00:44:47,371 --> 00:44:49,291
Vjetar? Ovo je tebi vjetar?

587
00:44:50,373 --> 00:44:51,013
Vjetar...

588
00:44:51,931 --> 00:44:53,391
... u Chicagu zimi...

589
00:44:55,258 --> 00:44:58,408
Moras mu okrenuti ledja,
ili ti reze obraze.

590
00:44:58,392 --> 00:44:59,492
Oduzima ti dah.

591
00:45:03,744 --> 00:45:05,444
Imamo najstariji hrast...

592
00:45:05,983 --> 00:45:07,383
... u obje Caroline.

593
00:45:08,842 --> 00:45:10,702
Imate nesto bolje od toga?

594
00:46:25,015 --> 00:46:26,815
Samo ti zelim biti blizu.

595
00:46:56,107 --> 00:46:57,097
Pazi, prasina.

596
00:47:01,663 --> 00:47:03,455
Pogledala je moje planove...

597
00:47:03,495 --> 00:47:05,185
... nije rekla ni rijec.

598
00:47:06,384 --> 00:47:08,654
Tjedan poslije bio je na platnu.

599
00:47:09,825 --> 00:47:11,565
Ovo je trebao biti prvi.

600
00:47:14,444 --> 00:47:17,504
Dizajniranje i izgradnja
vlastitih brodova...

601
00:47:17,689 --> 00:47:19,079
... to je bio plan.

602
00:47:21,313 --> 00:47:23,703
Ovo je trebao biti
brod uzorak...

603
00:47:23,908 --> 00:47:26,178
... i nikad ga ne bismo prodali.

604
00:47:27,755 --> 00:47:29,375
A kad ces ga dovrsiti?

605
00:47:33,981 --> 00:47:36,021
Dvije ga godine nisam taknuo.

606
00:47:38,020 --> 00:47:38,890
Jednog dana.

607
00:47:39,537 --> 00:47:39,817
Da.

608
00:47:41,745 --> 00:47:42,615
Jednog dana.

609
00:47:45,185 --> 00:47:47,061
Vodit ces me na jedrenje na njemu?

610
00:47:47,699 --> 00:47:50,969
Iza rta, gdje ce me vjetar
smrtno prestrasiti?

611
00:47:55,106 --> 00:47:56,856
Veceras nece biti vjetra.

612
00:47:59,603 --> 00:48:00,813
Uvjeren si u to?

613
00:48:03,072 --> 00:48:04,232
Ribarev sam sin.

614
00:48:05,362 --> 00:48:06,472
Gledas prognozu.

615
00:48:10,939 --> 00:48:13,039
Hoces veceras jedriti sa mnom?

616
00:48:15,488 --> 00:48:17,408
Za nekoliko se dana vracam.

617
00:48:19,092 --> 00:48:22,642
To ne mogu promijeniti,
jer sin mi se vraca kuci.

618
00:48:22,958 --> 00:48:25,518
Ne znam ima li ovo smisla.
Mozda...

619
00:48:39,581 --> 00:48:40,621
o je pogreska.

620
00:48:41,565 --> 00:48:43,605
Dopustiti da kusa tvoju kavu.

621
00:48:44,150 --> 00:48:45,890
Sinoc joj je bila dobra.

622
00:48:46,317 --> 00:48:47,947
Samo je bila pristojna.

623
00:48:48,729 --> 00:48:50,769
Nikomu nije dobra, vjeruj mi.

624
00:48:51,406 --> 00:48:52,216
Budi dobar.

625
00:48:55,894 --> 00:48:56,704
O, Gospode.

626
00:48:57,715 --> 00:48:58,575
Sto je sad?

627
00:49:03,708 --> 00:49:04,638
Ostani miran.

628
00:49:13,293 --> 00:49:14,543
U redu, stani ondje!

629
00:49:14,931 --> 00:49:16,181
Mici mi se s puta!

630
00:49:16,202 --> 00:49:18,078
Ovdje nisi dobrodosao, Johnny.

631
00:49:17,383 --> 00:49:18,633
Maknite se s puta! Obojica!

632
00:49:19,551 --> 00:49:20,881
Sud te opet odbio?

633
00:49:21,505 --> 00:49:24,007
- Ovo te se ne tice, Dodge.
- Rijeseno je.

634
00:49:24,190 --> 00:49:25,760
Ne, zelimo samo slike.

635
00:49:25,819 --> 00:49:27,695
Dio su naseg zivota ovdje, Marta.

636
00:49:27,865 --> 00:49:29,315
Vidite ih jedino vi.

637
00:49:29,778 --> 00:49:31,758
Ljudi bi ih trebali vidjeti.

638
00:49:32,200 --> 00:49:33,480
Molim te, Garrete.

639
00:49:34,102 --> 00:49:36,302
Od nje si nam samo to ostavio.

640
00:49:37,767 --> 00:49:40,894
Prvi put si me nazvao
njezinim ubojicom, Hank.

641
00:49:40,536 --> 00:49:41,396
Bar u lice.

642
00:49:42,642 --> 00:49:44,518
Zaboga, nitko je nije ubio.

643
00:49:43,884 --> 00:49:47,011
Ostavio ju je samu
kad je bila bolesna i slaba.

644
00:49:46,480 --> 00:49:48,981
- Htjela je doci kuci k nama!
- Ovo je bio njezin dom!

645
00:49:49,411 --> 00:49:50,661
Sad joj ubija i majku.

646
00:49:51,208 --> 00:49:53,710
Svaki dan slusam kako joj se
srce slama.

647
00:49:53,019 --> 00:49:54,895
Dao sam vam sve njezino
sto sam mogao.

648
00:49:54,536 --> 00:49:56,576
Slike! Sad imas drugu zensku!

649
00:49:57,191 --> 00:49:59,641
- Zasto ti je stalo?
- Pasji sine!

650
00:49:59,828 --> 00:50:01,328
Ne mijesaj se u ovo.

651
00:50:01,701 --> 00:50:02,391
Makni se!

652
00:50:06,839 --> 00:50:08,409
Naslikala ih je ovdje.

653
00:50:08,946 --> 00:50:10,456
Objesila ih je ovdje.

654
00:50:10,768 --> 00:50:13,798
Posljednja ih je dirala!
I tako ce ostati!

655
00:50:15,713 --> 00:50:17,103
Ovo zelite, zar ne?

656
00:50:18,562 --> 00:50:20,438
Ako je izrezem,
svi cete imati po dio.

657
00:50:22,084 --> 00:50:23,959
Svatko moze dobiti dio nje!

658
00:50:23,834 --> 00:50:24,994
Spusti to, tata.

659
00:50:25,341 --> 00:50:26,031
Makni se!

660
00:50:28,801 --> 00:50:29,501
Gospode...

661
00:50:30,938 --> 00:50:33,148
... zar vam ona samo ovo znaci?

662
00:50:35,527 --> 00:50:38,857
Nesto oko cega cete se svadjati?
Pogledajte se!

663
00:50:39,272 --> 00:50:41,192
Sve troje imate krvave oci!

664
00:50:41,706 --> 00:50:43,096
To je za Catherine?

665
00:50:43,803 --> 00:50:47,413
Ili da se mozete busati u prsa
kao gomila majmuna?

666
00:50:47,435 --> 00:50:49,311
K vragu, ovo te se ne tice.

667
00:50:49,796 --> 00:50:51,176
I ja sam je volio.

668
00:50:51,761 --> 00:50:53,851
I zelim je po necemu pamtiti.

669
00:50:54,122 --> 00:50:55,752
Dio ovoga ce dostajati.

670
00:51:01,877 --> 00:51:03,207
Ona bi mrzila ovo!

671
00:51:04,300 --> 00:51:05,550
Mrzila bi to, Hank.

672
00:51:05,715 --> 00:51:07,591
Dodge ima pravo.
Mrzila bi ovo...

673
00:51:07,109 --> 00:51:08,569
... vise od umiranja!

674
00:51:29,106 --> 00:51:29,916
Ludi ljudi.

675
00:51:32,149 --> 00:51:34,009
Oni su samo pola problema.

676
00:51:36,015 --> 00:51:38,045
Vidio si ih. Cuo sto govore.

677
00:51:38,958 --> 00:51:41,928
No i ti svoju polovicu
dosta dobro nosis.

678
00:54:14,484 --> 00:54:15,804
Ovo ti je u redu?

679
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:25,190
Prije tebe...

680
00:54:30,458 --> 00:54:33,898
... nisam mislio da cu s nekim
opet biti blizak.

681
00:54:35,322 --> 00:54:35,962
Katkad...

682
00:54:43,993 --> 00:54:45,563
Jos je osjecam. Ona...

683
00:54:46,526 --> 00:54:47,456
... je ovdje.

684
00:54:50,168 --> 00:54:52,088
Ne zelim te varati, heresa.

685
00:55:53,894 --> 00:55:55,704
Pojest ces cijelu vrecicu?

686
00:55:56,276 --> 00:55:58,026
Zasto imas dvije vrecice?

687
00:55:22,970 --> 00:55:23,900
Za streljivo.

688
00:56:04,261 --> 00:56:04,721
Cekaj.

689
00:56:08,641 --> 00:56:09,801
Ovdje je sjajno.

690
00:57:10,409 --> 00:57:11,659
Vani je bilo lijepo.

691
