732
01:00:07,435 --> 01:00:10,075
... kao teret, gusiti njezine ambicije.

733
01:00:13,000 --> 01:00:14,040
Kako je umrla?

734
01:00:16,643 --> 01:00:18,863
Trudnoca ju je potpuno iscrpila.

735
01:00:21,537 --> 01:00:24,867
Srusila se kod roditelja.
Zadrzali su je ondje.

736
01:00:24,122 --> 01:00:26,982
Garret je otisao onamo i
provalio vrata.

737
01:00:29,026 --> 01:00:29,946
Odnio ju je.

738
01:00:31,285 --> 01:00:32,675
Ona je bila sretna.

739
01:00:34,533 --> 01:00:37,503
Brinuo se za nju najbolje
sto je mogao...

740
01:00:38,837 --> 01:00:40,877
... oko mjesac dana. I tad...

741
01:00:41,207 --> 01:00:41,957
Samo se...

742
01:00:44,149 --> 01:00:44,969
... predala.

743
01:00:52,838 --> 01:00:55,698
Sad znas zasto Garret
ne govori previse.

744
01:00:57,519 --> 01:00:59,559
Jer njegov stari ne prestaje.

745
01:00:59,870 --> 01:01:01,090
Mozemo sad jesti?

746
01:01:10,247 --> 01:01:11,937
Trebas srusiti koji zid.

747
01:01:11,824 --> 01:01:13,574
Ovdje je prevelika guzva.

748
01:01:13,492 --> 01:01:14,742
Ne mogu si to priustiti.

749
01:01:15,537 --> 01:01:16,637
Mozemo to sami.

750
01:01:17,460 --> 01:01:19,030
Izgledalo bi kao brod.

751
01:01:19,942 --> 01:01:20,872
Dodaj palubu.

752
01:01:21,651 --> 01:01:22,641
Nekoliko soba.

753
01:01:22,680 --> 01:01:24,370
Zasto? Kanis se useliti?

754
01:01:29,577 --> 01:01:32,467
Ni u snu.
No svidjelo bi ti se, je li?

755
01:01:32,375 --> 01:01:33,626
Imat ces me na oku.

756
01:01:33,839 --> 01:01:36,340
Boji se da se ne vratim
starim navikama.

757
01:01:36,302 --> 01:01:37,692
Hoce li tko kolaca?

758
01:01:38,092 --> 01:01:39,342
Pio sam kao smuk.

759
01:01:39,915 --> 01:01:42,365
Unistio si zdravlje.
o nije tajna.

760
01:01:41,787 --> 01:01:43,877
Nije ni razlog da se ponosis.

761
01:01:45,246 --> 01:01:47,122
Dva piva na dan su mi granica.

762
01:01:47,769 --> 01:01:49,169
Da promijenimo temu?

763
01:01:56,000 --> 01:01:58,630
Tema je promjena.
Ljudi se mijenjaju.

764
01:01:58,055 --> 01:01:59,605
Cak i ti. o je tema.

765
01:02:01,637 --> 01:02:02,567
Dobra vecera.

766
01:02:06,896 --> 01:02:08,772
Ti si bila najbolja u njoj.

767
01:02:08,920 --> 01:02:13,110
Da sam oko 150 g. mladji,
morala bi se cuvati, mlada damo.

768
01:02:15,299 --> 01:02:15,699
Kamo?

769
01:02:17,923 --> 01:02:19,783
Pojest cu slatko na plazi.

770
01:02:20,039 --> 01:02:20,499
Hvala.

771
01:02:28,116 --> 01:02:29,096
Draga sam mu.

772
01:02:31,728 --> 01:02:32,648
Da. On je...

773
01:02:33,183 --> 01:02:34,353
... dobar covjek.

774
01:02:36,367 --> 01:02:38,397
Rekao je da si ti gnjavator.

775
01:02:43,661 --> 01:02:45,511
Salim se. o sam ja rekla.

776
01:02:47,588 --> 01:02:48,338
Ima pravo.

777
01:02:51,210 --> 01:02:53,480
Bila si najbolje na ovoj veceri.

778
01:02:54,996 --> 01:02:56,206
I u ovom danu...

779
01:02:59,206 --> 01:03:00,656
... i u ovoj godini.

780
01:03:05,474 --> 01:03:07,164
Da je bar jednostavnije.

781
01:03:09,279 --> 01:03:10,489
Da je bar lakse.

782
01:03:14,060 --> 01:03:15,030
I zao mi je.

783
01:04:02,806 --> 01:04:04,676
Ne ocekujem cvijece, ali...

784
01:04:05,177 --> 01:04:07,037
... hocemo li se bar cuti?

785
01:04:07,447 --> 01:04:07,847
Pa...

786
01:04:09,043 --> 01:04:10,553
... cuj, ja sam se...

787
01:04:11,548 --> 01:04:12,778
... nadao cvijecu.

788
01:04:20,537 --> 01:04:22,227
Mogla bih zivjeti ovdje.

789
01:04:25,421 --> 01:04:27,297
Nisam to rekla da te prestrasim.

790
01:04:27,447 --> 01:04:29,367
Prestrasila sam te, zar ne?

791
01:04:35,024 --> 01:04:36,594
Doci ces me posjetiti?

792
01:04:38,137 --> 01:04:39,657
Mislis u unutrasnjost?

793
01:04:40,193 --> 01:04:41,823
Ne idem u unutrasnjost.

794
01:04:42,616 --> 01:04:43,546
Imamo jezero.

795
01:04:44,599 --> 01:04:45,589
Veliko jezero.

796
01:04:47,143 --> 01:04:50,753
Dobro. Ja cu se vratit
svome poslu i svome sinu...

797
01:04:52,117 --> 01:04:53,977
... a ti me samo zaboravi.

798
01:04:55,719 --> 01:04:56,469
Svaki dan.

799
01:05:02,260 --> 01:05:03,950
Imam tvoj broj, mornaru.

800
01:05:04,855 --> 01:05:06,355
I ti imas moj. Pa...

801
01:05:50,865 --> 01:05:51,445
'Djenja.

802
01:06:50,339 --> 01:06:52,609
- I sto je tad bilo?
- Poslije.

803
01:06:53,006 --> 01:06:54,926
Lutalica se vraca. Kako si?

804
01:06:56,088 --> 01:06:57,898
Da? Rijesila si misteriju?

805
01:06:59,436 --> 01:07:00,836
Nije bilo misterije.

806
01:07:01,737 --> 01:07:03,607
Izgubio je zenu, Catherine.

807
01:07:04,483 --> 01:07:05,733
Bila je umjetnica.

808
01:07:06,793 --> 01:07:08,933
Mrtva je, ali on je jos voli.

809
01:07:08,808 --> 01:07:11,068
Dobro. I sto, to je kraj price?

810
01:07:11,718 --> 01:07:13,458
U osnovi da. Nema price.

811
01:07:14,191 --> 01:07:17,031
Bas kao da je...
Jesam li ja to rekao?

812
01:07:17,517 --> 01:07:17,917
Tako!

813
01:07:18,841 --> 01:07:20,981
Pa-pa, na put. Dosta je bilo.

814
01:07:24,764 --> 01:07:25,454
Zalis li?

815
01:07:27,602 --> 01:07:28,402
Ni za cim.

816
01:07:28,884 --> 01:07:29,634
Ne? Dobro.

817
01:07:33,014 --> 01:07:34,284
I? Kakva je bila?

818
01:07:39,415 --> 01:07:41,325
Bila je divna i krhka i...

819
01:07:42,925 --> 01:07:44,335
... sjajna umjetnica.

820
01:07:45,480 --> 01:07:46,460
I posvuda je.

821
01:07:47,596 --> 01:07:48,866
Svuda je po kuci.

822
01:07:49,438 --> 01:07:50,308
U radionici.

823
01:07:51,718 --> 01:07:52,968
Cijeli je grad volio.

824
01:07:53,438 --> 01:07:54,588
On je jos voli?

825
01:07:56,175 --> 01:07:57,335
Jos nije otisla.

826
01:08:04,648 --> 01:08:06,458
Za tebe. Veoma zanimljivo.

827
01:09:03,047 --> 01:09:04,457
Istrazivanje, heresa.

828
01:09:04,380 --> 01:09:04,950
Ja sam:

829
01:09:07,514 --> 01:09:08,034
Garret:

830
01:09:09,487 --> 01:09:09,887
Znam.

831
01:09:12,795 --> 01:09:14,255
Oprosti, bio sam: : :

832
01:09:15,663 --> 01:09:16,713
Zavrsavam brod:

833
01:09:18,576 --> 01:09:19,326
Svoj brod:

834
01:09:21,343 --> 01:09:22,963
Samo sam ti htio reci:

835
01:09:23,694 --> 01:09:24,614
Kako si ti:?

836
01:09:27,437 --> 01:09:28,887
jedni su bili mirni.

837
01:09:33,044 --> 01:09:33,974
Nisam znao...

838
01:09:34,926 --> 01:09:36,206
... sto bih rekao.

839
01:09:37,826 --> 01:09:38,746
Jos ne znam.

840
01:09:40,319 --> 01:09:41,309
Trebas pomoc:?

841
01:09:43,901 --> 01:09:45,231
Racunao sam na to.

842
01:09:47,482 --> 01:09:48,122
Pitanje::

843
01:09:49,344 --> 01:09:52,664
Je li nasa veza bila usputna
ili nesto drugo:?

844
01:09:52,764 --> 01:09:53,814
Mozda pocetak:?

845
01:09:55,583 --> 01:09:57,513
Samo odgovori, bez pritiska.

846
01:10:01,900 --> 01:10:04,240
Plejboj si koji hvata turistkinje?

847
01:10:04,770 --> 01:10:05,750
Samo mi je...

848
01:10:07,060 --> 01:10:09,740
... bilo stalo do dvije zene u zivotu.

849
01:10:10,418 --> 01:10:11,758
Do Catherine i... ?

850
01:10:12,840 --> 01:10:14,230
Neke cure iz grada:

851
01:10:14,356 --> 01:10:14,876
Lajave.

852
01:10:15,872 --> 01:10:16,452
Nasilne.

853
01:10:18,650 --> 01:10:19,110
Hvala.

854
01:10:21,723 --> 01:10:24,273
Nazvao si samo da mi kazes za brod?

855
01:10:25,701 --> 01:10:26,691
Nedostajes mi.

856
01:10:28,722 --> 01:10:29,942
Sve mi nedostaje.

857
01:10:35,307 --> 01:10:37,347
Zasto me ne dodjes posjetiti?

858
01:10:39,862 --> 01:10:42,072
To je samo posjet: Ne obecanje.

859
01:10:44,004 --> 01:10:45,334
Je li to dovoljno?

860
01:10:46,629 --> 01:10:49,539
Mislis da sam zagrizla za to,
ali nisam.

861
01:10:49,814 --> 01:10:51,374
Bojim se koliko i ti.

862
01:10:52,582 --> 01:10:54,092
I ti meni nedostajes.

863
01:10:57,210 --> 01:10:58,130
U redu. Kad?

864
01:11:01,067 --> 01:11:02,107
Kad da dodjem?

865
01:11:03,926 --> 01:11:04,386
Jucer.

866
01:11:06,777 --> 01:11:08,637
Ne dolazis brodom, zar ne?

867
01:11:09,705 --> 01:11:11,805
Jet skijama? Jedreci na dasci?

868
01:11:23,104 --> 01:11:24,154
Budi pristojan.

869
01:11:25,312 --> 01:11:26,122
Imas kartu?

870
01:11:28,171 --> 01:11:29,271
Dakako da imam.

871
01:11:31,174 --> 01:11:33,050
Na odjeci imam izvezeno ime.

872
01:11:33,066 --> 01:11:34,986
I imam kovanicu za telefon.

873
01:11:35,997 --> 01:11:37,737
A dar za njezino dijete?

874
01:11:39,079 --> 01:11:41,229
Kupi ga u ducanu na aerodromu.

875
01:11:42,030 --> 01:11:43,830
Nemoj se tuci ili slicno.

876
01:11:45,603 --> 01:11:46,173
Evo ga.

877
01:11:47,211 --> 01:11:49,301
Na vrijeme, kao i tvoj stari.

878
01:11:49,297 --> 01:11:50,547
Nemoj ozlijediti ledja.

879
01:11:50,997 --> 01:11:52,277
Pij svoje tablete.

880
01:11:53,073 --> 01:11:57,683
Po mom racunu, u hladnjaku trebaju
ostati dva piva kad se vratim.

881
01:11:58,567 --> 01:12:01,087
Zalostan posao, brojanje tudjih piva.

882
01:12:01,549 --> 01:12:04,677
Nagovoris li Kennyja ili djecu
turista da ti kupuju pivo...

883
01:12:05,080 --> 01:12:06,300
... saznat cu to.

884
01:12:07,532 --> 01:12:08,982
Pazim na dva okruga.

885
01:12:11,836 --> 01:12:13,526
Mala te dobro zakvacila.

886
01:12:15,692 --> 01:12:17,432
Kako si postao tako zao?

887
01:12:18,276 --> 01:12:20,076
Vidimo se za tjedan dana.

888
01:12:21,562 --> 01:12:22,022
Vraga!

889
01:12:24,941 --> 01:12:27,791
Neces kad ti je karta ovdje
na sjedalu!

890
01:12:38,431 --> 01:12:39,241
Dobar psic.

891
01:13:04,874 --> 01:13:06,734
Mislim da je stigao, mama.

892
01:13:13,593 --> 01:13:14,873
Nekako si zivcana.

893
01:13:15,446 --> 01:13:15,966
Doista?

894
01:13:16,890 --> 01:13:18,580
Izgledam sjajno, zar ne?

895
01:13:20,544 --> 01:13:22,114
Htjela sam reci dobro.

896
01:13:27,707 --> 01:13:28,457
Stigao si.

897
01:13:35,367 --> 01:13:35,767
Udji.

898
01:13:41,626 --> 01:13:45,076
Mislim da je razocaran jer nemas
kapetansku kapu.

899
01:13:45,715 --> 01:13:47,395
To je ocekivao. Zar ne?

900
01:13:47,823 --> 01:13:48,223
Udji.

901
01:13:57,457 --> 01:14:01,127
Ne znam je li prikladno
za decka tvoje dobi, ali...

902
01:14:01,447 --> 01:14:02,137
Super je.

903
01:14:02,758 --> 01:14:03,218
Hvala.

904
01:14:05,202 --> 01:14:06,312
Lijepo, Garrete.

905
01:14:12,436 --> 01:14:14,296
Sad je u fazi unistavanja.

906
01:14:15,041 --> 01:14:17,071
Mislim da je to nesto musko.

907
01:14:20,749 --> 01:14:21,799
Garrete, hvala.

908
01:14:23,039 --> 01:14:24,319
Ona mrzi slatkise.

909
01:14:25,420 --> 01:14:26,350
Doista cudno.

910
01:14:27,201 --> 01:14:27,721
Istina?

911
01:14:31,108 --> 01:14:32,908
Jest, ali lijepo od tebe.

912
01:14:34,457 --> 01:14:34,977
Pardon.

913
01:14:40,786 --> 01:14:42,886
Hvala. Ovo sam doista zeljela.

914
01:14:53,208 --> 01:14:55,128
Zacijelo si umoran, zar ne?

915
01:14:58,631 --> 01:14:59,881
Nadam se da ce ovo biti u redu.

916
01:14:59,730 --> 01:15:00,710
Bit ce dobro.

917
01:15:03,619 --> 01:15:05,079
Zelim reci, savrseno.

918
01:15:05,754 --> 01:15:09,324
Sutra navecer Jason spava
kod prijatelja. ako da...

919
01:15:10,680 --> 01:15:11,660
Sto to znaci?

920
01:15:14,089 --> 01:15:14,609
Zavezi.

921
01:15:18,515 --> 01:15:21,145
- Znam da ovo nije romanticno.
- Sto?

922
01:15:20,276 --> 01:15:21,527
Ovo je moj zivot.

923
01:15:21,853 --> 01:15:22,833
Ne, ovo je...

924
01:15:23,288 --> 01:15:24,048
... Iijepo.

925
01:15:24,967 --> 01:15:25,717
Lijepo je.

926
01:15:26,779 --> 01:15:28,229
Zelim da me upoznas.

927
01:15:29,934 --> 01:15:31,984
Samo svakodnevnu, obicnu mene.

928
01:15:34,575 --> 01:15:36,145
Mislis da me poznajes?

929
01:15:57,982 --> 01:15:58,552
Sto je?

930
01:15:59,316 --> 01:15:59,656
Sto?

931
01:16:02,705 --> 01:16:03,685
On nece doci.

932
01:16:07,649 --> 01:16:09,679
Ali ja sam presao dalek put.

933
01:16:15,716 --> 01:16:16,926
I ne znam zasto.

934
01:16:21,863 --> 01:16:23,533
Drago mi je sto si tu.

935
01:16:25,322 --> 01:16:27,522
I meni je drago sto sam ovdje.

936
01:16:46,288 --> 01:16:47,908
Jos malo i stigli smo.

937
01:17:01,489 --> 01:17:02,639
Cekaj. o je on?

938
01:17:03,046 --> 01:17:03,786
To je on.

939
01:17:07,380 --> 01:17:08,770
O, Boze! Ni rijeci.

940
01:17:09,427 --> 01:17:10,237
Hej, stari!

941
01:17:10,914 --> 01:17:12,124
Sto ti radis tu?

942
01:17:13,997 --> 01:17:15,267
Vlak je bio guba.

943
01:17:15,726 --> 01:17:17,656
Mogu se posluziti racunalom?

944
01:17:20,346 --> 01:17:22,096
Jason te htio iznenaditi.

945
01:17:23,073 --> 01:17:24,948
- Nadam se da je u redu.
- Sjajno.

946
01:17:25,567 --> 01:17:28,477
Samo na minutu,
onda se vracamo na vlak.

947
01:17:28,547 --> 01:17:30,047
On ga se boji, mama.

948
01:17:31,417 --> 01:17:32,567
Ne bojim ga se.

949
01:17:36,291 --> 01:17:37,281
Annie, Garret.

950
01:17:41,614 --> 01:17:42,714
Ovdje ja radim.

951
01:17:49,671 --> 01:17:50,541
Kakav komad!

952
01:17:50,974 --> 01:17:52,244
Bilo mi je drago.

953
01:17:58,290 --> 01:18:00,500
Sad te mogu zamisliti na poslu.

954
01:18:06,623 --> 01:18:08,499
Znaci to je on? o je Ahab?

955
01:18:08,851 --> 01:18:11,353
Da, to je on.
No nije kapetan Ahab.

956
01:18:11,304 --> 01:18:13,174
Nasmij mu se. Prijateljski.

957
01:18:14,866 --> 01:18:16,446
- Dragi ljudi.
- Znam.

958
01:18:16,818 --> 01:18:18,694
Smije joj se. ako je sladak.

959
01:18:19,169 --> 01:18:20,269
Daj budi dobra.

960
01:18:21,917 --> 01:18:25,007
Tako si negativan.
Ne zelis da bude sretna?

961
01:18:26,831 --> 01:18:29,221
Ostatak zivota smrdjet ce po ribi.

962
01:18:30,718 --> 01:18:32,518
Ne znam sto sam ocekivao.

963
01:18:33,181 --> 01:18:34,821
Mislim, nisam shvatio...

964
01:18:34,993 --> 01:18:36,853
... da su svi tako bliski.

965
01:18:37,099 --> 01:18:39,319
Theresa, ovo ce te iznenaditi...

966
01:18:40,050 --> 01:18:42,920
... no pudl je ipak
najpopularniji pas...

967
01:18:44,507 --> 01:18:47,008
- Drago mi je upoznati vas.
- Takodjer.

968
01:18:47,165 --> 01:18:48,395
- Lina.
- Jasone.

969
01:18:50,674 --> 01:18:53,474
Jason vodi Garreta
u jedrenje po gradu.

970
01:18:54,572 --> 01:18:55,792
Doista? ako brzo?

971
01:18:56,210 --> 01:18:57,890
Ako se prije ne izgubi.

972
01:18:57,971 --> 01:19:00,001
Znam da je u blizini jezero.

973
01:19:01,105 --> 01:19:02,085
On osjeca to.

974
01:19:02,550 --> 01:19:05,240
Osjecajan.
Ako se uvalite u nevolje...

975
01:19:03,841 --> 01:19:06,191
... svakako me...
Nazovite novine.

976
01:19:09,743 --> 01:19:11,863
- Zelis kormilariti?
- Svakako.

977
01:19:11,382 --> 01:19:12,362
i si kapetan.

978
01:19:13,111 --> 01:19:14,451
Moras drzati smjer.

979
01:19:15,950 --> 01:19:17,000
Ravno naprijed.

980
01:19:21,302 --> 01:19:21,822
Izvoli.

981
01:19:29,789 --> 01:19:31,189
- Kako si?
- Dobro.

982
01:19:34,550 --> 01:19:36,420
Cijelo drustvo. Bok, Lenny.

983
01:19:36,179 --> 01:19:38,229
- 'Djenja, mama.
- Zabavi se.

984
01:19:38,946 --> 01:19:40,996
- Pozdravi mamu.
- Vidimo se!

985
01:20:11,877 --> 01:20:13,557
Nisam navikla da si tu.

986
01:20:16,863 --> 01:20:18,253
U redu je, Garrete.

987
01:20:24,717 --> 01:20:25,587
Lijepo je...

988
01:20:26,193 --> 01:20:27,953
... medju tvojim stvarima.

989
01:20:30,049 --> 01:20:31,499
Jesi li to ocekivao?

990
01:20:34,179 --> 01:20:34,929
Ugodno je.

991
01:20:56,935 --> 01:20:58,455
Cinis me samosvjesnom.

992
01:21:01,361 --> 01:21:02,171
Sto gledas?

993
01:21:03,579 --> 01:21:05,209
Theresu u njezinu domu.

994
01:21:10,122 --> 01:21:11,532
Obicna svakodnevna...

995
01:21:12,698 --> 01:21:13,518
... Theresa.

996
01:21:30,764 --> 01:21:31,224
Cekaj.

997
01:21:35,384 --> 01:21:36,314
Doista sam...

998
01:21:37,899 --> 01:21:40,289
... htjela da ovo bude kako treba.

999
01:21:39,791 --> 01:21:43,241
Htjela sam pospremiti sobu
i upaliti svijecu i...

1000
01:21:47,046 --> 01:21:48,616
I moram se istusirati.

1001
01:21:49,926 --> 01:21:50,976
Garrete, cekaj.

1002
01:23:39,575 --> 01:23:40,375
1, 2, 3...

1003
01:23:43,615 --> 01:23:44,535
... 4, 5, 6!

1004
01:23:46,668 --> 01:23:48,544
- aj je bio dobar.
- Bojim se.

1005
01:23:51,574 --> 01:23:52,844
Ja se tako bojim.

1006
01:23:55,542 --> 01:23:56,812
Ovo je bilo jako.

1007
01:23:57,425 --> 01:23:59,355
Idem se istusirati. Napokon.

1008
01:24:03,917 --> 01:24:04,907
Cekaj. Samo...

1009
01:25:43,615 --> 01:25:45,305
Pronadjena Poruka U Boci

1010
01:25:46,578 --> 01:25:47,628
Draga Catherine

1011
01:25:53,539 --> 01:25:55,059
Neces vjerovati sto...

1012
01:26:01,454 --> 01:26:02,674
O, Boze, Garrete.

1013
01:26:03,693 --> 01:26:04,673
Otkud ti ovo?

1014
01:26:09,484 --> 01:26:10,414
Pronasla sam.

1015
01:26:11,253 --> 01:26:13,003
Kako to mislis, pronasla?

1016
01:26:12,780 --> 01:26:14,060
Pronasla na obali.

1017
01:26:16,402 --> 01:26:17,452
Garrete, cekaj.

1018
01:26:18,672 --> 01:26:19,882
Doslo je k meni.

1019
01:26:20,708 --> 01:26:22,048
Moras mi vjerovati.

1020
01:26:23,008 --> 01:26:23,938
Vjerovati ti?

1021
01:26:24,881 --> 01:26:28,921
Morala sam upoznati autora
toga. Morala sam upoznati tebe.

1022
01:26:28,779 --> 01:26:31,281
- Htjela sam ti prije reci.
- Kako si me mogla pronaci?

1023
01:26:32,637 --> 01:26:35,787
Pronasla sam sve poruke
i u njima tragove...

1024
01:26:36,350 --> 01:26:37,160
Sve poruke?

1025
01:26:41,224 --> 01:26:44,976
Sve su pronadjene. Ljudi su
procitali clanak i pisali nam.

1026
01:26:44,268 --> 01:26:46,768
Kunem se Bogom, kanila sam ti reci.

1027
01:26:46,893 --> 01:26:47,943
Garrete, cekaj.

1028
01:26:48,869 --> 01:26:49,799
Moram odavde.

1029
01:26:53,417 --> 01:26:54,467
Garrete, cekaj!

1030
01:26:56,469 --> 01:26:57,919
Zasto si to ucinila?

1031
01:26:58,729 --> 01:26:59,249
Zasto?!

1032
01:27:02,291 --> 01:27:03,691
Bila si znatizeljna?

1033
01:27:05,282 --> 01:27:08,409
- To je prokleto istrazivanje?
- Ne, zaljubljujem se u tebe!

1034
01:27:08,337 --> 01:27:11,464
Prvo u pisma, a kad sam
te upoznala, i u tebe!

1035
01:27:11,410 --> 01:27:13,430
I zao mi je! Bojala sam se!

1036
01:27:13,548 --> 01:27:16,676
Bojala sam se da cu te otjerati
kazem li ti!

1037
01:27:16,641 --> 01:27:18,201
Kao sto to sad cinim!

1038
01:27:19,887 --> 01:27:20,347
Cekaj!

1039
01:27:21,953 --> 01:27:23,633
Ma sto mislio o meni...

1040
01:27:23,602 --> 01:27:25,478
... ma sto se dogodilo, zelim da znas...

1041
01:27:24,905 --> 01:27:26,781
... koliko mi je stalo do tebe.

1042
01:27:27,276 --> 01:27:29,196
Ne bi trebalo biti vazno...

1043
01:27:29,220 --> 01:27:31,440
... sto nas je spojilo, Garrete.

1044
01:27:32,385 --> 01:27:35,512
Bacio sam ta pisma u more za nju,
ne za tebe!

1045
01:27:36,067 --> 01:27:37,943
Ne za tvoje prijatelje s posla!

1046
01:27:37,950 --> 01:27:38,350
Znam.

1047
01:27:39,009 --> 01:27:41,149
Svi su znali za mene, zar ne?

1048
01:27:40,881 --> 01:27:42,041
Sve o Catherine?

1049
01:27:42,744 --> 01:27:45,364
Ta su mi tri pisma promijenila zivot.

1050
01:27:46,622 --> 01:27:48,497
- Nisam htjela da to novine objave.
- Dva pisma.

1051
01:27:52,109 --> 01:27:55,919
- Moras mi vjerovati.
- Poslao sam dva pisma Catherine.

1052
01:27:54,092 --> 01:27:54,552
Molim?

1053
01:27:57,045 --> 01:27:58,785
Imam sva pisma. Sva tri.

1054
01:28:01,512 --> 01:28:02,962
Gdje je trece pismo?

1055
01:28:05,093 --> 01:28:06,363
U onoj je ladici?

1056
01:28:15,573 --> 01:28:16,273
Catherine?

1057
01:28:43,062 --> 01:28:44,812
Svim brodovima na moru...

1058
01:28:45,201 --> 01:28:46,481
... i svim lukama:

1059
01:28:47,623 --> 01:28:48,793
Mojoj obitelji...

1060
01:28:49,475 --> 01:28:51,815
... svim prij eljima i neznancima:

1061
01:28:52,243 --> 01:28:53,983
Ovo je poruka i molitva:

1062
01:28:55,886 --> 01:28:59,856
Poruka je da su me moja
putovanja naucila vaznoj istini.

1063
01:29:00,648 --> 01:29:03,558
Vec sam imala ono
sto svi drugi traze...

1064
01:29:04,678 --> 01:29:06,538
... a malo tko ikad nadje.

1065
01:29:06,663 --> 01:29:08,293
Jednu osobu koju sam...

1066
01:29:08,749 --> 01:29:10,689
... rodjena voljeti zauvijek.

1067
01:29:12,016 --> 01:29:14,466
Osobu poput mene, s Outer Banksa...

1068
01:29:15,892 --> 01:29:18,652
... i tajanstvenu poput modrog Atlantika.

1069
01:29:20,625 --> 01:29:22,975
Osobu prepunu jednostavnih blaga...

1070
01:29:23,464 --> 01:29:25,694
... kovaca svoje srece, samoukog.

1071
01:29:28,248 --> 01:29:30,338
Luku u kojoj sam uvijek doma.

1072
01:29:31,474 --> 01:29:33,054
Nikakvi zli vjetrovi...

1073
01:29:34,100 --> 01:29:37,720
... ni neka mala smrt ne
mogu unistiti tog covjeka.

1074
01:29:41,357 --> 01:29:44,977
Molim se da svatko na
svijtu upozna takvu ljubav...

1075
01:29:46,823 --> 01:29:48,333
... i da ga izlijeci.

1076
01:29:49,511 --> 01:29:53,421
Cuje li tko moju molitvu,
ponistit ce se svi grijesi...

1077
01:29:53,253 --> 01:29:55,173
... i sve za cime zalite...

1078
01:29:56,653 --> 01:29:58,633
... i nece vise biti gnjeva.

1079
01:30:00,337 --> 01:30:01,437
Molim te, Boze.

1080
01:30:02,545 --> 01:30:02,945
Amen.

1081
01:30:15,193 --> 01:30:17,523
Nikad nisam znao sto je napisala.

1082
01:30:20,128 --> 01:30:20,588
Ona...

1083
01:30:22,275 --> 01:30:25,025
... se poslije toga dana nije oporavila.

1084
01:30:27,322 --> 01:30:29,832
Osusio sam je. Pokusao je zagrijati.

1085
01:30:31,220 --> 01:30:32,900
Odveo sam je u bolnicu.

1086
01:30:33,163 --> 01:30:34,033
Ona nikad...

1087
01:30:40,316 --> 01:30:42,176
Umrla je tri dana poslije.

1088
01:30:45,537 --> 01:30:48,337
Stalno mislim da tog dana nije izasla...

1089
01:30:48,265 --> 01:30:49,835
Garrete, ona je znala.

1090
01:30:53,252 --> 01:30:54,172
Rekla je to.

1091
01:30:56,345 --> 01:31:00,315
" Ni mala smrt ne moze unistiti
tog covjeka. " Znala je.

1092
01:31:06,225 --> 01:31:06,805
Zelim...

1093
01:31:08,036 --> 01:31:09,206
... zadrzati ovo.

1094
01:32:20,900 --> 01:32:23,170
Oprosti. Bi li radije bila sama?

1095
01:32:30,637 --> 01:32:31,617
Je li nazvao?

1096
01:32:35,113 --> 01:32:36,973
No ostavila sam mu poruku.

1097
01:32:39,266 --> 01:32:40,996
Rekla sam da mi je zao.

1098
01:32:42,340 --> 01:32:44,370
I zamolila sam ga da nazove.

1099
01:32:45,891 --> 01:32:47,041
Pa onda i hoce.

1100
01:32:50,458 --> 01:32:51,738
Lina, sjecas se...

1101
01:32:53,288 --> 01:32:55,558
... na sto sam se uvijek zalila?

1102
01:32:57,085 --> 01:33:00,055
Svaki put kad sam ti plakala
zbog Davida?

1103
01:32:59,860 --> 01:33:00,610
Sjecas se?

1104
01:33:03,026 --> 01:33:04,496
Iskrenost. Povjerenje.

1105
01:33:07,056 --> 01:33:08,446
Tako sam se bojala.

1106
01:33:12,928 --> 01:33:13,558
Ja ne...

1107
01:33:15,227 --> 01:33:17,327
Zaljubljujem se u Garreta i...

1108
01:33:19,826 --> 01:33:21,702
Pola mozga govori mi :
" Kazi mu"...

1109
01:33:21,700 --> 01:33:23,690
... a druga polovica govori :

1110
01:33:26,014 --> 01:33:27,594
" Cekaj. Nece shvatiti.

1111
01:33:29,281 --> 01:33:30,531
Cekaj pravi trenutak.

1112
01:33:31,204 --> 01:33:33,074
Cekaj prave rijeci. " Znas?

1113
01:33:35,000 --> 01:33:36,460
Uprskala sam. Samo...

1114
01:33:37,290 --> 01:33:39,910
Ubila sam to postavsi ono sto mrzim :

1115
01:33:40,097 --> 01:33:40,857
Lazljivica.

1116
01:33:41,226 --> 01:33:42,336
Nisi lazljivica.

1117
01:33:43,833 --> 01:33:45,223
Ali za njega jesam.

1118
01:33:47,708 --> 01:33:50,848
I ne vjerujem da ce mi ikad
moci vjerovati.

1119
01:33:51,555 --> 01:33:53,995
Ne shvacas da svi imamo male lazi?

1120
01:33:54,536 --> 01:33:56,236
Male neizgovorene istine?

1121
01:33:57,529 --> 01:34:00,779
Moras vjerovati u to
da ce i on to shvatiti.

1122
01:34:03,377 --> 01:34:04,007
Ne znam.

1123
01:34:07,447 --> 01:34:09,117
Ne znam moze li on to.

1124
01:34:11,712 --> 01:34:15,912
Vidjela sam njegovu bol.
Drzao je njezino pismo i citao ga.

1125
01:34:16,606 --> 01:34:17,596
Vidjela sam...

1126
01:34:18,256 --> 01:34:19,656
... toliko boli i...

1127
01:34:24,257 --> 01:34:25,997
On je toliko voli, znas?

1128
01:34:29,377 --> 01:34:30,007
Ne znam.

1129
01:36:03,331 --> 01:36:07,301
Rekao si da ako ikad pozelim
nesto napisati za novine...

1130
01:36:08,569 --> 01:36:09,489
Ne salis se.

1131
01:36:12,853 --> 01:36:13,883
On je u tome?

1132
01:36:14,511 --> 01:36:14,911
Nije.

1133
01:36:16,759 --> 01:36:17,629
Druge price.

1134
01:36:18,440 --> 01:36:19,310
Dobre price.

1135
01:36:20,750 --> 01:36:22,080
Bilo je i vrijeme.

1136
01:36:24,526 --> 01:36:27,096
Kad ljude povrijedis, oni se zatvore.

1137
01:36:27,598 --> 01:36:28,988
Dok bol ne nestane?

1138
01:36:30,540 --> 01:36:31,170
Ne znam.

1139
01:36:32,564 --> 01:36:35,654
Mozda naucis to prihvatiti
kao i sve drugo.

1140
01:36:38,721 --> 01:36:41,401
Kako komadice cepa
u casi finog vina.

1141
01:36:41,417 --> 01:36:43,167
Ne zelis propustiti vino.

1142
01:36:44,511 --> 01:36:45,601
To je u ovome?

1143
01:36:47,147 --> 01:36:48,467
To o cepu u vinu?

1144
01:36:49,569 --> 01:36:49,969
Nije.

1145
01:36:51,076 --> 01:36:52,526
Dobro. Gadilo mi se.

1146
01:36:59,356 --> 01:37:02,336
Mozda svi mi pisemo
svoje zivotne price...

1147
01:37:03,366 --> 01:37:05,756
... izmisljajuci ih iz dana u dan.

1148
01:37:06,326 --> 01:37:10,706
No cini se da drugi imaju
zivote vec oblikovane i planirane...

1149
01:37:11,057 --> 01:37:12,177
... neizbjezne...

1150
01:37:13,235 --> 01:37:15,115
... savrsene poput kruznice.

1151
01:39:20,437 --> 01:39:20,957
Otvori.

1152
01:39:22,921 --> 01:39:23,441
Polako.

1153
01:39:30,021 --> 01:39:32,011
- Ovo je uzbudljivo.
- Jest.

1154
01:39:33,807 --> 01:39:36,309
Cudesno Putovanje
Izgubljen i pronadjen na moru

1155
01:39:36,035 --> 01:39:37,615
Prva stranica!
Sjajno!

1156
01:39:40,371 --> 01:39:41,301
Hvala, stari.

1157
01:39:42,172 --> 01:39:43,392
Mogu ga izrezati?

1158
01:39:43,617 --> 01:39:44,197
Svakako.

1159
01:39:45,205 --> 01:39:47,125
- Ovo je u redu?
- Sjajno.

1160
01:39:49,295 --> 01:39:50,405
Savrseno. Hvala.

1161
01:39:58,186 --> 01:39:58,996
Vasa posta.

1162
01:39:59,691 --> 01:40:00,151
Hvala.

1163
01:40:01,970 --> 01:40:02,890
I drugi put.

1164
01:40:20,119 --> 01:40:21,049
Draga heresa.

1165
01:40:21,656 --> 01:40:22,906
Mnogo sam razmisljao o tebi.

1166
01:40:23,630 --> 01:40:26,132
Da nije bilo tebe, ne bih znao
Catherineine posljednje rijeci.

1167
01:40:25,757 --> 01:40:28,258
Mislim da sam sve sto osjecam
stavio u ovaj brod.

1168
01:40:28,301 --> 01:40:29,801
Porinut cu ga 25-og.

1169
01:40:30,783 --> 01:40:34,393
Nadam se da ces ga uskoro vidjeti.
Voli te Garret.

1170
01:40:33,318 --> 01:40:33,838
Lijepo.

1171
01:40:36,361 --> 01:40:38,391
Svidja mi se sto si ucinila.

1172
01:40:39,343 --> 01:40:41,844
- Veoma minimalisticki.
- Lijepo od vas sto ste svratili.

1173
01:40:41,673 --> 01:40:45,943
Da, donosim darove za tvoj
novi ured u telefonskoj govornici.

1174
01:40:46,202 --> 01:40:48,077
- Smijem objesiti?
- Tako slatko.

1175
01:40:48,593 --> 01:40:48,993
Znam.

1176
01:40:56,375 --> 01:40:58,355
Nikad neces pogoditi tko je.

1177
01:41:03,466 --> 01:41:04,686
Doimas se sretno.

1178
01:41:06,030 --> 01:41:06,890
Sve u redu?

1179
01:41:07,627 --> 01:41:07,967
Aha.

1180
01:41:13,906 --> 01:41:14,426
Smijem?

1181
01:41:19,848 --> 01:41:22,238
Ucinis li nesto divlje i
glupo...

1182
01:41:24,356 --> 01:41:26,226
... dokazat ces samo jedno.

1183
01:41:26,401 --> 01:41:27,371
A sto je to?

1184
01:41:28,825 --> 01:41:31,085
Da je on jedan sretan sin mora.

1185
01:41:37,604 --> 01:41:39,764
To je citat Charlieja Toschija.

1186
01:41:56,728 --> 01:41:59,288
Netko ce misliti da gore susis gace.

1187
01:42:04,267 --> 01:42:05,377
Lijepo izgledas.

1188
01:42:06,557 --> 01:42:07,647
Da, i to boli.

1189
01:42:37,045 --> 01:42:38,565
Prekrasan je, Garrete.

1190
01:42:39,568 --> 01:42:40,498
Hvala, Marta.

1191
01:42:43,251 --> 01:42:43,941
Sredi ih!

1192
01:42:50,363 --> 01:42:52,063
Sjajno uradjeno, Garrete.

1193
01:43:20,737 --> 01:43:21,667
Za Catherine.

1194
01:43:22,089 --> 01:43:23,019
Za Catherine.

1195
01:43:25,020 --> 01:43:26,010
Boze, zelim...

1196
01:43:30,362 --> 01:43:32,392
Zelim da je ona danas ovdje.

1197
01:43:37,250 --> 01:43:38,170
I svaki dan.

1198
01:45:22,280 --> 01:45:24,480
ata je rekao da si bila ondje.

1199
01:45:24,967 --> 01:45:26,587
Volio bih da sam znao.

1200
01:45:27,953 --> 01:45:29,833
Iznenadjenje. Glupa zamisao.

1201
01:45:30,392 --> 01:45:31,082
Ne, ja...

1202
01:45:32,762 --> 01:45:34,612
Drago mi je sto te vidim.

1203
01:45:36,781 --> 01:45:39,511
- Drago mi je sto si dosla.
- I meni.

1204
01:45:40,130 --> 01:45:42,050
Vidjela sam brod. Divan je.

1205
01:45:43,010 --> 01:45:43,530
Sjajan.

1206
01:45:45,901 --> 01:45:47,521
Drago mi je zbog tebe.

1207
01:45:48,262 --> 01:45:49,242
Zelis li uci?

1208
01:46:10,987 --> 01:46:11,567
Oprosti.

1209
01:46:14,029 --> 01:46:16,369
Povrijedio sam te svojim rijecima.

1210
01:46:20,825 --> 01:46:23,675
Cula sam sto mi nisi mogao
osobno reci.

1211
01:46:25,831 --> 01:46:27,631
Ili sto nisam mogla cuti.

1212
01:46:29,160 --> 01:46:30,200
I sad shvacam.

1213
01:46:32,110 --> 01:46:34,020
Divno je to kako je volis.

1214
01:46:34,613 --> 01:46:36,353
Ne, ne moras nista reci.

1215
01:46:37,647 --> 01:46:39,917
To me natjeralo da te pronadjem.

1216
01:46:45,541 --> 01:46:46,791
Onda ostani sa mnom.

1217
01:46:47,261 --> 01:46:48,191
Dodji unutra.

1218
01:46:48,717 --> 01:46:50,117
Ostani koliko zelis.

1219
01:46:51,107 --> 01:46:55,486
Razmisljala sam o tome. Razmisljala sam
o mnogo toga sjedeci vani.

1220
01:46:55,218 --> 01:46:56,488
I ne mogu ostati.

1221
01:46:56,603 --> 01:46:57,063
Zasto?

1222
01:46:58,282 --> 01:47:00,158
Jer ako mozes, ti ces doci k meni...

1223
01:47:01,019 --> 01:47:04,279
... kad bude vrijeme.
Ako ne bude, u redu je.

1224
01:47:04,939 --> 01:47:05,979
Jer ja necu...

1225
01:47:07,350 --> 01:47:09,110
... zaliti nijednu minutu.

1226
01:47:10,148 --> 01:47:10,838
Ni jednu.

1227
01:47:14,818 --> 01:47:15,398
'Djenja.

1228
01:47:26,254 --> 01:47:27,764
Ne zelim te izgubiti.

1229
01:47:31,046 --> 01:47:31,856
Onda nemoj.

1230
01:47:50,364 --> 01:47:52,934
Zasto uvijek sjedis na istome mjestu?

1231
01:47:53,539 --> 01:47:55,415
Zasto je vazno gdje sjedim?

1232
01:47:55,178 --> 01:47:59,088
Znatizeljan sam. Poceo si
sjediti ovdje prije 10, 11 g.

1233
01:47:59,015 --> 01:47:59,535
Zaboga!

1234
01:48:00,673 --> 01:48:02,243
Nekad si sjedio ondje.

1235
01:48:19,411 --> 01:48:20,981
Daj decku salicu kave.

1236
01:48:28,180 --> 01:48:29,290
Izgledas grozno.

1237
01:48:32,024 --> 01:48:32,774
Dobro sam.

1238
01:48:34,682 --> 01:48:35,782
Pronasao si je?

1239
01:48:41,019 --> 01:48:42,289
Pustio si da ode.

1240
01:48:43,644 --> 01:48:45,520
Ne zelim razgovarati o tome.

1241
01:48:45,385 --> 01:48:47,255
- Cuj, ja sam...
- Odlazi.

1242
01:48:54,196 --> 01:48:55,066
Odlucila je.

1243
01:48:56,559 --> 01:48:58,435
- Koga vraga hoces?
- Upornost.

1244
01:48:58,338 --> 01:49:00,618
Poludi. Posizi.
Bori se, zaboga!

1245
01:49:00,894 --> 01:49:02,864
Proveo si jedan dan s njom.

1246
01:49:04,861 --> 01:49:06,761
Cak i ne znas tko je ona.

1247
01:49:10,162 --> 01:49:10,682
Koji...

1248
01:49:11,292 --> 01:49:11,872
Chicago.

1249
01:49:12,432 --> 01:49:13,772
Tri minute. Nazovi.

1250
01:49:18,263 --> 01:49:20,243
To ti je posljednja prilika.

1251
01:49:30,846 --> 01:49:32,296
Dakako da je otisla.

1252
01:49:32,994 --> 01:49:34,094
Nije ona glupa.

1253
01:49:36,341 --> 01:49:37,592
Mislis da se zeli postaviti
izmedju tebe i...

1254
01:49:40,992 --> 01:49:44,119
- Ni meni nije sve jasno!
- A komu, do vraga, jest?

1255
01:49:43,688 --> 01:49:46,815
Mislis da mi je lako gledati
drugu zenu u tvojoj kuci?

1256
01:49:45,257 --> 01:49:46,237
Nije mi lako.

1257
01:49:46,986 --> 01:49:48,256
Reci cu ti jedno.

1258
01:49:48,767 --> 01:49:51,269
Dao bih milijun dolara
da vidim kako je grlis...

1259
01:49:50,804 --> 01:49:52,054
... i rjesavas sve putem.

1260
01:49:52,635 --> 01:49:53,615
Dosta o tome!

1261
01:49:54,385 --> 01:49:55,905
- Dosta?
- Da. Dosta!

1262
01:49:55,993 --> 01:49:56,513
Samo...

1263
01:49:59,545 --> 01:50:00,945
... zaboravi sve to.

1264
01:50:01,948 --> 01:50:02,578
Ne mogu!

1265
01:50:07,655 --> 01:50:08,995
Ne mogu zaboraviti!

1266
01:50:10,475 --> 01:50:11,865
Zasto, k vragu, ne?

1267
01:50:13,283 --> 01:50:14,663
Jer ti si moj sin.

1268
01:50:17,954 --> 01:50:20,164
- To se tebe ne tice.
- Molim?

1269
01:50:20,378 --> 01:50:22,108
Rekoh da te se ne tice!

1270
01:50:23,725 --> 01:50:24,475
Okreni se.

1271
01:50:26,493 --> 01:50:27,243
Okreni se.

1272
01:50:29,872 --> 01:50:30,742
Stisni saku.

1273
01:50:31,684 --> 01:50:32,204
Stisni!

1274
01:50:34,106 --> 01:50:35,086
Sad me udari!

1275
01:50:35,470 --> 01:50:37,560
Udari me u lice, pasji skote!

1276
01:50:41,208 --> 01:50:42,298
Ne tice me se?

1277
01:50:42,837 --> 01:50:44,507
Moj me se sin ne tice?

1278
01:50:45,910 --> 01:50:47,130
Sto drugo imam...

1279
01:50:49,788 --> 01:50:51,298
... sto mi je blisko?

1280
01:50:52,475 --> 01:50:53,865
ko je drugi ikad...

1281
01:50:54,813 --> 01:50:56,153
... stajao uz mene?

1282
01:50:57,083 --> 01:50:59,823
Mislis da ne poznajem tvoju bol?
Znam!

1283
01:50:58,874 --> 01:51:03,014
Ja sam odgovoran za dio nje.
Mislis da to mogu zaboraviti?

1284
01:51:05,835 --> 01:51:08,962
Kad je otisla u New York,
mogao si otici s njom...

1285
01:51:08,155 --> 01:51:10,657
... a ja sam bio ovdje.
Bolestan, pijan, na ledjima...

1286
01:51:11,263 --> 01:51:13,013
... unistavao sam i tebe.

1287
01:51:14,597 --> 01:51:17,627
Mozda je za vas dvoje
moglo biti drukcije.

1288
01:51:21,770 --> 01:51:23,570
Ja nisam ostao zbog tebe.

1289
01:51:24,985 --> 01:51:26,545
Ovo je ono sto jesam.

1290
01:51:26,796 --> 01:51:28,666
Ovo mjesto. Ovamo pripadam.

1291
01:51:30,929 --> 01:51:34,056
Ona se vratila jer je otkrila
da i ona ovamo pripada.

1292
01:51:33,522 --> 01:51:34,972
Izabrala je za sebe.

1293
01:51:38,122 --> 01:51:40,212
Boze, volio sam je zbog toga.

1294
01:51:42,345 --> 01:51:42,795
I ja.

1295
01:51:46,009 --> 01:51:47,819
Sad ti izaberi. Izaberi...

1296
01:51:48,746 --> 01:51:51,616
... izmedju jucer i sutra.
Izaberi jedno.

1297
01:51:53,295 --> 01:51:54,445
I ostani uz to!

1298
01:51:55,503 --> 01:51:56,893
A ja cu zavezati...

1299
01:51:57,793 --> 01:51:59,653
... i ostaviti te na miru.

1300
01:52:33,299 --> 01:52:35,339
" Uvijek ces znati gdje si...

1301
01:52:35,640 --> 01:52:36,970
... i gdje je dom.

1302
01:52:40,047 --> 01:52:41,267
Voli te heresa. "

1303
01:53:09,410 --> 01:53:10,520
Draga Catherine:

1304
01:53:43,168 --> 01:53:44,738
Ides na otvoreno more?

1305
01:53:45,937 --> 01:53:46,927
Da, gospodine.

1306
01:53:49,071 --> 01:53:50,641
Valjda znas sto radis.

1307
01:53:52,285 --> 01:53:53,445
Sve sam smislio.

1308
01:55:02,963 --> 01:55:03,773
Hej, stari.

1309
01:55:05,039 --> 01:55:06,609
Vrijeme je da ustanes.

1310
01:55:09,100 --> 01:55:10,140
Jos jedan dan.

1311
01:59:08,575 --> 01:59:10,795
Zovu ga Gradonacelnik 43. Ulice.

1312
01:59:10,458 --> 01:59:13,328
Sladak je. Svakoga poznaje.
Svima pomaze.

1313
01:59:15,861 --> 01:59:18,181
Bitno je da mu je 70. rodjendan.

1314
01:59:19,595 --> 01:59:22,695
Oprosti sto prekidam, heresa.
Poziv za tebe.

1315
01:59:21,824 --> 01:59:23,074
Mozes primiti poruku?

1316
01:59:23,249 --> 01:59:23,939
Hitno je.

1317
01:59:26,800 --> 01:59:27,320
Pardon.

1318
01:59:29,131 --> 01:59:30,631
Javi se u mom uredu.

1319
01:59:31,125 --> 01:59:31,755
Jase je?

1320
01:59:37,558 --> 01:59:38,548
Hej, djevojko?

1321
01:59:39,643 --> 01:59:40,223
Bolje...

1322
01:59:45,444 --> 01:59:47,894
... reci ovo dok jos mogu govoriti:

1323
01:59:49,666 --> 01:59:51,986
Na pucini je bio brod u nevolji.

1324
01:59:53,453 --> 01:59:54,853
Obitelj, njih troje.

1325
01:59:55,590 --> 01:59:56,990
Garret je pokusao...

1326
01:59:58,581 --> 02:00:00,151
Pokusao je pomoci i...

1327
02:00:02,844 --> 02:00:04,354
Gadno je. Potonuo je.

1328
02:00:07,282 --> 02:00:08,442
Kako to mislite?

1329
02:00:09,359 --> 02:00:10,749
Krenuo je za njima.

1330
02:00:11,180 --> 02:00:13,800
Dvoje je izvukao.
Ali on je potonuo.

1331
02:00:15,963 --> 02:00:17,003
Tako mije zao.

1332
02:00:20,522 --> 02:00:22,312
To je sve sto mogu reci:

1333
02:00:23,687 --> 02:00:24,267
'Djenja:

1334
02:00:32,602 --> 02:00:33,522
O, moj Boze!

1335
02:02:38,326 --> 02:02:39,546
Teska su vremena.

1336
02:02:40,270 --> 02:02:40,670
Udji.

1337
02:02:50,057 --> 02:02:51,917
Ovo sam pronasao na brodu.

1338
02:02:52,448 --> 02:02:53,848
U njegovoj kabanici.

1339
02:03:17,912 --> 02:03:19,082
Draga Catherine::

1340
02:03:19,896 --> 02:03:21,772
Zivot mije poceo kad sam te upoznao...

1341
02:03:21,882 --> 02:03:25,635
... i mislio sam da je zavrsio
kad te nisam uspio spasiti.

1342
02:03:25,261 --> 02:03:29,461
Mislio sam da nas uspomena na
tebe oboje odrzava na zivotu.

1343
02:03:29,911 --> 02:03:31,191
No pogrijesio sam.

1344
02:03:31,986 --> 02:03:33,862
Zena po imenu Theresa
pokazala mije...

1345
02:03:33,952 --> 02:03:36,454
... da ako sam dovoljno
hrabar da otvorim srce...

1346
02:03:36,384 --> 02:03:40,124
... mogu opet voljeti, ma kako
velika bila moja tuga.

1347
02:03:40,059 --> 02:03:42,679
Pokazala mije da sam samo napola ziv.

1348
02:03:43,527 --> 02:03:45,397
Prestrasilo me i zaboljelo.

1349
02:03:45,859 --> 02:03:49,999
I nisam znao koliko mi treba
dok nisam gledao kako odlazi.

1350
02:03:53,674 --> 02:03:57,874
Kadje avion poletio, osjetio
sam kako se nesto u meni lomi.

1351
02:03:56,289 --> 02:03:57,149
I znao sam.

1352
02:03:58,234 --> 02:03:59,984
Trebao sam je zaustaviti.

1353
02:03:59,882 --> 02:04:01,802
Trebao sam je pratiti kuci.

1354
02:04:02,029 --> 02:04:05,009
A sutra cu odjedriti
do vjetrovitog rta...

1355
02:04:05,133 --> 02:04:07,223
... i oprostit cu se od tebe.

1356
02:04:08,735 --> 02:04:10,185
Otici cu toj zeni...

1357
02:04:10,925 --> 02:04:13,445
... i pokusati osvojiti njezino srce.

1358
02:05:24,764 --> 02:05:27,265
Ako uspijem,
znam da ces me blagosloviti.

1359
02:05:27,105 --> 02:05:28,735
I blagosloviti sve nas.

1360
02:05:29,374 --> 02:05:30,064
Ako ne...

1361
02:05:30,810 --> 02:05:33,312
... onda sam i dalje blagoslovljen
jer sam volio...

1362
02:05:33,628 --> 02:05:35,028
... dvaput u zivotu.

1363
02:05:35,755 --> 02:05:37,005
Ona mije to omogucila.

1364
02:05:37,525 --> 02:05:41,278
A ako ti kazem da je volim
koliko sam volio i tebe...

1365
02:05:41,800 --> 02:05:43,430
... onda ces sve znati.

1366
02:05:45,423 --> 02:05:47,463
Pocivaj u miru, ljubavi moja.

1367
02:05:47,620 --> 02:05:48,140
Garret.

1368
02:06:17,897 --> 02:06:20,587
Ako su neki zivoti savrsena kruznica...

1369
02:06:21,347 --> 02:06:26,157
... drugi uzimaju oblik koji ne mozemo
predvidjeti ni uvijek shvatiti.

1370
02:06:27,452 --> 02:06:29,842
Gubitak je bio dio moga putovanja.

1371
02:06:30,881 --> 02:06:33,141
No i pokazao mi je sto vrijedi.

1372
02:06:35,674 --> 02:06:39,114
Kao i ljubav na kojoj
mogu jedino biti zahvalna.

